translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_61ae9591:

    # s alert_irritated "Kyou, I can see I have sent you into a state of decision paralysis, but I cannot continue to function like this." with dissolve
    s alert_irritated "Kyou, puedo ver que te he enviado a un estado de parálisis de decisión, pero no puedo continuar así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:607
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_9a49fcc9:

    # s "Just knowing that you can have me shift between myself and my alter ego with but a phrase will always be deeply disturbing to me should it remain."
    s "El solo saber que puedes hacerme alternar entre mi alter ego y yo con una frase siempre será perturbador para mí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:608
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_fd703020:

    # s "To say nothing of the fact that your penlight should never be used again after tonight."
    s "Sin mencionar el hecho de que tu linterna no debe ser usada en nadie más después de esta noche."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:609
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_94423005:

    # s uniform alert_annoyed_right "So... allow me to make this easier for you, for everyone's sake." with dissolve
    s uniform alert_annoyed_right "Así que... permíteme facilitarte las cosas, por el bien de todos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:610
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_763f99e8:

    # "Sayori pauses to draw a shuddered breath, a hand at her stomach."
    "Sayori hace pausa para exhalar estremecidamente con una mano en su estómago."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:611
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_99549136:

    # s "I will permit you to put me back into a state of hypnotic trance once more, with the purpose of mitigating the damage you have inflicted upon my mind."
    s "Permitiré que me pongas en un estado de trance hipnótico una vez más, con el propósito de mitigar el daño que le que le has infligido a mi mente."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:621
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_999e51e2:

    # s uniform_handup "While in trance, you will remove both your suggestions compelling me to sleep, and the ones pertaining to me switching personalities." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup "Mientras esté en trance, removerás tanto las sugestiones que me obligan a dormir, como las correspondientes a mi cambio de personalidades." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:613
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_77b1983b:

    # "She pauses again and holds my gaze, and I'm practically compelled to nod at her."
    "Hace otra pausa mirándome a los ojos, y estoy prácticamente obligado a asentir con la cabeza."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:614
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_0abff1d6:

    # s alert_annoyed "Afterwards... you have two choices." with dissolve
    s alert_annoyed "Posteriormente... tienes dos opciones." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:615
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_8b3da8ef:

    # s "One, you simply wake me from trance and that will be the end of it."
    s "Una, sencillamente me despiertas del trance y todo se habrá acabado."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:625
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_e3ab2859:

    # s alert_irritated "What you did with [alt_name] will always be a part of me now, I suppose." with dissolve
    s alert_irritated "Lo que hiciste con [alt_name] siempre será parte de mí, supongo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:626
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_ac426ef7:

    # s uniform alert_annoyed_right "But if I understand correctly she will have no means of taking back control ever again." with dissolve
    s uniform alert_annoyed_right "Pero, si entendí correctamente, no tendrá ningún medio para retomar el control." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:618
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c51ce454:

    # ks "It's as good as killing her."
    ks "Sería igual a matarla."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:619
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_e34316a7:

    # "I can't help it. I have to say it out loud that this is what we'd be doing if I went along with this."
    "No puedo evitarlo. Tengo que decir en voz alta que eso es lo que haríamos si acepto ese plan."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:620
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_9ec3e952:

    # "But Sayori simply sighs and continues."
    "Pero Sayori simplemente suspira y continúa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:621
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_63d40322:

    # s uniform_folded alert_irritated "Or... or you work in a way to integrate [alt_name]'s consciousness with my own." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded alert_irritated "O... puedes buscar el modo de integrar la consciencia de [alt_name] en la mía." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:622
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_cdef5a42:

    # n shocked_side "H-Huh?!" with dissolve
    n shocked_side "¡¿E-eh?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:623
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c3139ee9:

    # "I only don't cry out myself because Nozomi beats me to it."
    "No exclamo solo porque Nozomi lo hace primero."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:624
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_9124f173:

    # "She'd been silent for so long, contemplatively listening with a pained expression, but this is..."
    "Lleva mucho tiempo en silencio, escuchando atentamente con una expresión de dolor, pero esto es..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:625
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_1bbc123d:

    # n sad_side "Sayori, you... you CAN'T! You can't let him do this!" with dissolve
    n sad_side "Sayori, no... ¡NO PUEDES! ¡No puedes dejar que haga eso!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:626
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_61b3b5a3:

    # s alert_concerned "If you were around to say that to me five days ago, Nozomi, you might have had a point." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned "Si hubieras estado ahí para decirme lo mismo hace cinco días, Nozomi, tal vez habrías tenido un punto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:636
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_8283b51c:

    # s uniform_handup "But [alt_name]... I understand her to be a separate consciousness. And now she is in the same limbo I was until just a few hours ago." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup "Pero [alt_name]... entiendo que es una consciencia independiente. Y ahora se encuentra en el mismo limbo en el que yo estaba hace solo unas cuantas horas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:637
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_3ff035f4:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "I would not wish such a state on anyone, let alone someone who is, to put it simply, another me." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "No le desearía dicho estado a nadie, mucho menos a quien es, por así decirlo, otra yo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:629
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_4544322f:

    # n "But... but if you let her back into your life she'll wreck your plans won't she?"
    n "Pero... pero si dejas que regrese a tu vida, destruirá tus planes, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:640
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a29a0622:

    # n sad_closed "Everything you've worked for..." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Todo en lo que has trabajado..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:641
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_cfdae7ee:

    # s alert_concerned "I would almost certainly have to change my plans to accommodate her. But as I believe she said, she has a right to exist." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned "Tengo casi completa certeza de que sí tendría que cambiar mis planes para albergarla. Pero, como creo que ella dijo, tiene derecho a existir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:642
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_f334fce2:

    # s uniform alert_sleep "She deserves to be considered." with dissolve
    s uniform alert_sleep "Merece ser considerada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:633
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_7ae9b139:

    # "Sayori then looks to me with a sneer."
    "En ese momento, Sayori me mira con una mueca."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:634
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_51034d51:

    # s alert_smirk_right "So which will it be, Kyou?" with dissolve
    s alert_smirk_right "Entonces, ¿qué elijes, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:635
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_f50a2fc5:

    # s "Ruin my life? Or destroy hers?"
    s "¿Arruinar mi vida? ¿O destruir la suya?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:584
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_240e4d07:

    # ns shocked "Why? Why are you leaving this up to him, Sayori?"
    ns shocked "¿Por qué? ¿Por qué lo dejas en sus manos, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:641
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_88a21b51:

    # "Nozomi gestures to her friend pleadingly while Sayori sets herself up on the couch."
    "Nozomi le suplica a su amiga, mientras que Sayori se acomoda en el sofá."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:642
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_3d9192d2:

    # s "Because this choice will be Kyou's burden to bear, not mine. Besides..."
    s "Porque esta elección será la carga de Kyou, no la mía. Además..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:643
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_f5e531a6:

    # scg alert_smile "I have been subject to his whims for this long. Why change now?" with dissolve
    scg alert_smile "He sido sujeto de estos caprichos por tanto tiempo. ¿Por qué cambiar ahora?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:645
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_af9cfcbd:

    # scg alert_stern "Now get started. I want us to finish this." with dissolve
    scg alert_stern "Ahora comienza. Quiero terminar con esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:645
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_d129afa7:

    # "... I haven't even decided what to do yet."
    "... Aún ni siquiera decido qué hacer."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:646
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_59097529:

    # "But as both girls glare at me, I hold my penlight aloft and start to pass the light across Sayori's waiting eyes."
    "Pero mientras las dos chicas me observan, sostengo mi linterna en lo alto y comienzo a pasar la luz por los ojos de Sayori."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:648
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_b5b18ad3:

    # ks frown "O-okay..."
    ks frown "E-está bien..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:649
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_7b2f7933:

    # "Shit, how do I even do this? I'm supposed to talk her calmly into a trance with so much tension?"
    "Mierda. ¿Y cómo voy a hacer esto? ¿Se supone que la guíe calmadamente al trance con tanta tensión?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:661
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_f52dee71:

    # ks "So... uh, just relax and look up into the light, Sayori."
    ks "Pues... Eh, solo relájate y mira la luz, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:654
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_4199157a:

    # ks "And as you stare... focus on the patterns that should be forming in your eyes." with dissolve
    ks "Y mientras miras... concéntrate en los patrones que se forman ante tus ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:656
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_874a6d48:

    # "Nervous as I am, and as tense as everyone seems to be, Sayori still seems content to follow along."
    "Por nervioso que esté, y por tensos que todos nos sintamos, Sayori me sigue tan bien como siempre."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:657
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_00fc95b3:

    # "So... I'll just try and do what I normally do and go from there."
    "Así que... solo intentaré hacer lo que normalmente hago y ver qué sale."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:658
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_dca0e8fa:

    # ks "Those patterns must feel so good to look at. So natural to focus on..."
    ks "Debe sentirse muy bien mirar esos patrones. Es muy natural concentrarse en ellos..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:660
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_86076ff2:

    # ks "And as you focus, you may start to feel a pull at the corners of your eyes..."
    ks "Y al concentrarte, tal vez empieces a sentir una fuerza tirando de tus ojos..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:663
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_96d3a93b:

    # ks neutral "A pull that starts to become stronger, ever so slightly, every time you... blink."
    ks neutral "Una fuerza que crece y crece, poco a poco, cada vez que... parpadeas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:664
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_e8ec0a38:

    # "I time that last word just as Sayori appears to blink naturally."
    "Digo esa última palabra justo cuando Sayori parpadea."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:665
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_86435912:

    # "And as I spare a quick side glance, I notice Nozomi seems to be studying the pair of us with a focused expression of her own."
    "Y al dar un rápido vistazo de soslayo, noto que Nozomi parece estudiarnos casi con la misma concentración."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:668
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_20e66db3:

    # ks "Just a little harder to keep your eyelids open, Sayori, as you focus on the light for me."
    ks "Es un poco más difícil mantener tus ojos abiertos, Sayori, al concentrarte en la luz."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:670
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a097c3cd:

    # ks "That's right... feeling that pull on your eyelids as you focus. Letting yourself focus deeply into the light for me."
    ks "Eso es... siente esa fuerza que tira de tus párpados mientras te concentras. Concéntrate profundamente en la luz."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:674
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_05918045:

    # ks "Feeling so focused. So deep. So relaxed."
    ks "Tan concentrada. Tan profundo. Tan relajada."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:676
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_ce97864f:

    # ks "So very comfortable to let yourself drift back into trance as your eyelids become heavier and heavier."
    ks "Entrando tan cómodamente en trance una vez más, tus párpados se ponen más y más pesados."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:678
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_1b4a925a:

    # ks "Heavier and heavier, Sayori. Consciously finding it so very hard to keep your eyes open, to keep focusing on the light for me."
    ks "Más y más pesados, Sayori. Conscientemente te das cuenta de lo difícil que es mantener tus ojos abiertos y seguir concentrándote en la luz."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:680
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_fc4fa03b:

    # ks "And that's okay. You can let your lead-heavy eyelids close and relax deep into trance for me now, Sayori, if you want to."
    ks "Y eso está bien. Puedes dejar que tus pesados ojos se cierren y entrar en un relajante trance, Sayori, si eso es lo que quieres."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:684
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_eaef8d2d:

    # ks "You can find yourself slipping back into sleep, ready to listen to my suggestions as I take you deeper... if you want to."
    ks "Puedes dormir otra vez, lista para escuchar mis sugestiones y dejarme llevarte más profundo... si eso es lo que quieres."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:686
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_e1aaeef2:

    # "As Sayori's head noticeably droops, I lean a little closer and speak to her gently." with longdissolve
    "Cuando Sayori deja caer su cabeza, me acerco un poco más y le hablo con gentileza." with longdissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:687
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_0f5f8539:

    # ks "Do you want to be taken deeper, Sayori?"
    ks "¿Quieres que te lleve más profundo, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:688
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_1f3daa1a:

    # "There's a pause. A little longer than I find comfortable."
    "Hay una pausa. Un poco más larga de lo que me gustaría."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:689
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_d6e4d348:

    # "But as I'm about to ask her again, her lips begin to part."
    "Pero cuando estoy a punto de repetir la pregunta, sus labios comienzan a separarse."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:690
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_28ef3a80:

    # scg alert_sleeptalk "Uh-huh..." with dissolve
    scg alert_sleeptalk "Ajá..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:692
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_956089b6:

    # "I start to smile, only to feel Nozomi's gaze boring into my side." with dissolve
    "Empiezo a sonreír, pero siento la mirada de Nozomi penetrándome." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:693
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a3d440ac:

    # "... I guess I'd better get started."
    "... Supongo que será mejor que comience."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:694
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_d2c64361:

    # ks "Very good, Sayori. Dropping deeper now, at my suggestion. Enjoying the sensation of going deeper, letting your mind become open and relaxed to my words."
    ks "Muy bien, Sayori. Cae más profundo ahora. Disfruta la sensación de caer más profundo, dejando que tu mente se relaje y se abra a mis palabras."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:695
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_2c683f16:

    # ks "Going deeper... and as you drop so deep, I want you to think about how you're compelled to blank your mind the moment you settle down to sleep every night."
    ks "Más profundo... y mientras caes, quiero que pienses cómo estás obligada a poner tu mente en blanco cuando te vas a dormir cada noche."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:696
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_ca8e1e94:

    # ks "And now, as you think about that, Sayori, I need you to realize that this is no longer true."
    ks "Y ahora que estás pensando en eso, Sayori, quiero que te des cuenta de que eso ya no es verdad."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:697
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_f533dcac:

    # ks "You will no longer be compelled to blank your mind completely when you try to sleep at night. What you do when you try to sleep is entirely up to you again."
    ks "Ya no estarás obligada a vaciar tu mente por completo cuando intentes dormir por las noches. Lo que hagas cuando intentes dormir dependerá enteramente de ti."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:698
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_6cbdd3cd:

    # ks "Do you understand, Sayori?"
    ks "¿Comprendes, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:699
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_28ef3a80_1:

    # scg alert_sleeptalk "Uh-huh..." with dissolve
    scg alert_sleeptalk "Ajá..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:701
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_b2ff09ec:

    # ks "Furthermore, you must realize that my saying \"become [alt_name]\", or \"become Sayori\" will no longer affect you in any unusual way." with dissolve
    ks "Además de eso, debes darte cuenta de que oírme decir \"conviértete en [alt_name] \" o \"conviértete en Sayori\" ya no te afectará de ninguna forma inusual." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:702
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_d3b78c2c:

    # ks "They will be simply as any other words. Understand, Sayori?"
    ks "Serán palabras como cualquier otra. ¿Comprendes, Sayori? "

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:703
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_9b36505b:

    # scg alert_sleeptalk "Uh-huh... understand..." with dissolve
    scg alert_sleeptalk "Ajá... comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:705
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_3fc574ae:

    # "I exchange looks with Nozomi and nod." with dissolve
    "Intercambio miradas con Nozomi y asiento con la cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:706
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_e980b2b4:

    # "If anything that's happened in the past week has proved anything, it's that what I told Sayori just now will absolutely ring true."
    "Si lo que ocurrió esta semana me ha demostrado algo, es que lo que acabo de decirle a Sayori se hará realidad sin ninguna duda."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:707
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c4226926:

    # "And that means [alt_name] is basically sealed away in Sayori's mind, with no way of resurfacing."
    "Y eso significa que [alt_name] está básicamente sellada en la mente de Sayori, sin ninguna forma de resurgir."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:653
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_0e89be86:

    # ns frown "{size=16}What're you waiting for?{/size}"
    ns frown "{size=16}¿Qué esperas?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:709
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_e6e66fcd:

    # "Nozomi hisses at me. She had been watching our hypnosis session with fascination up until now."
    "Nozomi me reclama. Ha estado observando fascinada nuestra sesión de hipnosis desde el comienzo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:710
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_8c3541d7:

    # "But having apparently finished removing Sayori's suggestions, she's anxious to have me wake her."
    "Pero habiendo aparentemente terminado de remover las sugestiones de Sayori, está impaciente de verla despertar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:711
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_bac07a42:

    # "Only I'm not done. As I look over Sayori's dormant form, I know I still have a decision to make."
    "Solo que aún no he terminado. Viendo la durmiente silueta de Sayori, sé que aún tengo una decisión que tomar..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:712
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a0ec2ed3:

    # "[alt_name]..."
    "[alt_name]..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:713
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_ae22a58c:

    # "[alt_name], I..."
    "[alt_name], yo..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:721
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_1679b8ad:

    # "Sayori never asked for any of this."
    "Sayori nunca pidió nada de esto."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:722
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_1104be3e:

    # "I had to talk her into letting me hypnotize her for fun, and now she's suffered for that."
    "Tuve que convencerla de dejarme hipnotizarla por diversión, y ahora está sufriendo por eso."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:723
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_9a5f96ff:

    # "Can I really expect her to carry [alt_name] for the rest of her life?"
    "¿Qué derecho tengo de hacerla cargar con [alt_name] por el resto de su vida?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:724
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_320e71d6:

    # "I wish there was another way, but..."
    "Desearía que hubiera otra forma, pero..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:725
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_cbfba282:

    # "[alt_name]... I'm sorry."
    "[alt_name]... Lo siento."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:726
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_07cfac08:

    # ks "That's great, Sayori. And now that these suggestions are completely gone from your mind, it's time to wake you up slowly."
    ks "Grandioso, Sayori. Y ahora que esas sugestiones se han ido de tu mente, es hora de que despiertes lentamente."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:727
