    # s alert_happy "Very well, then! So Nozomi, here is what I propose..."
    s alert_happy "¡Pues muy bien! Nozomi, esta es mi propuesta..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:879
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_fec97169:

    # "To be continued..."
    "Continuará..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:957
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bd39e652:

    # "Before I know it, I'm walking into the start of another school week."
    "Antes de darme cuenta estoy por comenzar otra semana de escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:958
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a294ec6f:

    # "That weekend I just had with Nozomi... I could almost believe I imagined it, surreal as it was."
    "El fin de semana que pasé con Nozomi... me cuesta no creer que lo imaginé; fue tan surreal."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:961
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7f11fec6:

    # "But she really did have me over at her house. And we really had all that fun together..."
    "Pero en verdad me invitó a su casa. Y en verdad compartimos todos esos momentos de diversión..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:963
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_10f0f7a9:

    # t "Now class, I hope you all remember you'll be doing your mock entrance exams in a couple days."
    t "Ahora, clase, espero que todos recuerden que sus exámenes simulacro serán en un par de días."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:964
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1e9340b9:

    # "Huh? What's our homeroom teacher saying?"
    "¿Eh? ¿Qué dijo el profesor?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:965
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9b03498a:

    # t "While these examinations will in no way impact upon your admittance to your college of choice..."
    t "Si bien estas pruebas no impactarán de ninguna forma su admisión a la universidad de su elección..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:966
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_69e899af:

    # "Oh... right. I guess I was supposed to study for those instead of... well, what we did."
    "Oh... cierto. Creo que se suponía que estudiara para esos en lugar de... bueno, lo que hicimos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:967
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f8b1bb85:

    # t "... It'll be your final chance to check your progress and readjust before the examinations proper, so DO take them seriously, people..."
    t "... Será su última oportunidad de evaluar su progreso y reajustarse antes de los exámenes verdaderos, así que tómenselos EN SERIO..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:972
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_da9f4c6f:

    # "As lunch rolls around once more, I lean forward a little as I watch Nozomi and her group pull themselves away from their seats."
    "Cuando llega nuevamente la hora del almuerzo, me inclino un poco hacia adelante, viendo a Nozomi y a su grupo levantarse de sus asientos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:980
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d9782b99:

    # "Nozomi is apologizing to Hiroko again for missing her tourney." with dissolve
    "Nozomi se disculpa con Hiroko una vez más por perderse su torneo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:981
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_41efb77c:

    # "Hiroko is really upset that Nozomi couldn't even be bothered to say that she wasn't coming."
    "Hiroko que está muy molesta de que Nozomi ni siquiera se molestara en decir que no iría."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:983
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_09612299:

    # "Hiroko being sad to the point of being on the verge of tears is unsettling to everyone, seeing how she normally reponds with explosive anger all the time." with dissolve
    "" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:984
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b41ac141:

    # "And Nozomi can only apologize again and tell Hiroko that something very important came up."
    ""

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:985
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3dbc9a55:

    # "Although when Sayori asks what that something could be, suspicions are aroused when Nozomi doesn't come up with anything."
    ""

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:986
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ddf3040a:

    # "It probably sets Nozomi's friend's minds to work given her behaviour last week, when she stayed up late and had no explanation for that either."
    ""

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:988
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fe297d66:

    # n "I can't apologize enough for yesterday, Hiroko." with dissolve
    n "No puedo expresar cuánto lo siento por lo de ayer, Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:989
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ad66fb6d:

    # h sleeptalk "Forget about it. 'Least you showed up in the end." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Ya olvídalo. Al menos te apareciste al final." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:991
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bb9ee857:

    # s uniform concerned "It still concerns me that this happened, Nozomi. It is unlike you to miss something like this without a very good reason." with dissolve
    s uniform concerned "Aun así me preocupa que haya ocurrido, Nozomi. Perderte algo así sin una buena razón parece impropio de ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:992
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_eab99f6c:

    # s "I do not wish to pry, but- {w=0.5}{nw}"
    s "No quisiera entrometerme, pero- {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:996
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_137c8556:

    # n frown_side "Then don't." with dissolve
    n frown_side "Pues no lo hagas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:997
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c4c527b1:

    # h uniform_arm frown_side "Shit, Nozo, she was just asking!" with dissolve
    h uniform_arm frown_side "¡Mierda, Nozo, solo era una pregunta!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:999
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f866d093:

    # n sad_closed "I... *sigh* I'm sorry. I've just been a bit on edge lately, that's all." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Yo... *suspiro* Lo siento. Es que he estado muy estresada últimamente, es todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1000
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a23e257d:

    # n sad_side "What with the... um, the exams." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Por... em... los exámenes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1002
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2cd9870a:

    # s concerned "Do you need assistance? We can go over a few things later if you'd like?" with dissolve
    s concerned "¿Necesitas asistencia? Podemos repasar un par de cosas más tarde si gustas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1003
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_97ca69b1:

    # n sad_closed "O-oh, no it's fine. I don't want to bother you about it." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "O-oh, no. Así está bien. No quiero molestarte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1004
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_970f7124:

    # s uniform "I would not consider it a bother-{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    s uniform "No es ninguna molestia-{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1005
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8856a522:

    # n sad_side "Really, it's fine. I've got this." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Estoy bien, de veras. Puedo con esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1008
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_321690ef:

    # n smile_side "But anyway, Hiroko, maybe I didn't catch everything yesterday but from what I saw you did pretty well out there." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Pero, en fin, Hiroko, tal vez no pude verlo todo ayer, pero por lo que sí presencié, lo hiciste muy bien allá afuera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1010
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9389d46f:

    # n sad_side "Do you... do you think it was enough for your scholarship?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿Crees... crees que sea suficiente para tu beca?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1011
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c11d15f8:

    # h irritated "Man, why're you asking me? I don't fucking know." with dissolve
    h irritated "Ay, ¿y a mí por qué me preguntas? Ni puta idea." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1012
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3aebb279:

    # s uniform sleep "My, we are all on edge today, aren't we." with dissolve
    s uniform sleep "Cielos, todas estamos estresadas hoy, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1013
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7c493b99:

    # s smile "Perhaps a spell on the rooftop will do you both some good. Clear your heads." with dissolve
    s smile "Quizá una visita a la azotea les haga bien. Despejar sus mentes un rato.." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1015
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2e4a83fb:

    # h sad_side "Geez, you hear that, Nozo? Sayori's telling us to go to the rooftop." with dissolve
    h sad_side "Ey, ¿oíste eso, Nozo? Sayori nos está diciendo que vayamos a la azotea." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1016
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3dbd4b90:

    # h sleep "That's how you know it's bad." with dissolve
    h sleep "Así de mal están las cosas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1061
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9074b221:

    # "An uneasy silence follows the three of them as they file out of the classroom." with dissolve
    "Siendo asechadas por un inquietante silencio, las tres abandonan el salón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1062
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_07b7cdfa:

    # "I wish I could follow them up there, but I know that's the last thing Nozomi wants right now."
    "Desearía poder ir con ellas, pero sé que, ahora mismo, eso es lo último que Nozomi quiere."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1065
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f86fe2b9:

    # "Still, I'll shoot Nozomi a text, see if she's coming over tonight."
    "Pero le enviaré un mensaje a Nozomi para ver si vendrá esta noche."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1068
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_12caf6b4:

    # "Nozomi responds in the affirmative, as she's keen to continue their play."
    ""

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1070
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1b29b148:

    # "If she meant what she said before, she won't leave me out of the loop this time."
    "Si lo que me dijo fue sincero, no me dejará colgado esta vez."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1072
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b1eb32f6:

    # "And it gives me a little comfort to find that after a few minutes I do get a text back." with vpunch
    "Y me causa algo de consuelo ver que, pocos minutos después, recibo su respuesta." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1073
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_89a43234:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"No sorry I need to study\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"No, lo siento tengo que estudiar\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1074
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_dd2865ef:

    # "And just like that I feel less comforted."
    "Y en un instante, mi consuelo se desploma."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1075
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b85366f0:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"You should too\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"Tu también deberías \"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1076
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fc60272d:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"Study?\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"¿Estudiar?\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1077
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8b1458c8:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"Yes\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"Sí\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1078
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f0848d0d:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"Maybe we could study together?\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"¿Tal vez podamos estudiar juntos?\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1079
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9857d74f:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"Kyou please\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"Kyou por favor\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1081
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_02ed98e9:

    # "I put my phone down at my desk and sigh."
    "Pongo mi teléfono en el escritorio y suspiro."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1082
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_25efcbb2:

    # "She's right, I guess. We'd probably distract each other from studying if the weekend was anything to go by."
    "Tiene razón, supongo. Probablemente nos distraeremos el uno al otro, viendo lo que pasó el fin de semana."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1083
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9c43c2e6:

    # "And I do probably need to step up my study game..."
    "Y yo también necesito acelerar el paso con mis estudios..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1084
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d8ee8e90:

    # "But damn, this is annoying."
    "Pero, diablos, qué fastidio."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1090
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_00762d8c:

    # "And I do need to think about it..."
    "Y además tengo que pensar..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1091
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b8f22961:

    # "What AM I gonna do when I get out of this school?"
    "¿QUÉ voy a hacer cuando salga de esta escuela?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1092
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9409b8d7:

    # "I've spent all year trying not to think about graduating, only for this to come up now and slap me in the face."
    "Pasé todo el año intentando no pensar en la graduación, solo para que esto venga a golpearme en la cara."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1094
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4872c23b:

    # "And what a time to have to think about it, right when I've been making headway with Nozomi."
    "Y qué buen momento para pensar en eso, justo cuando por fin estoy progresando con Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1095
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e6a7f23d:

    # "I don't want to think about any of this, dammit..."
    "No quiero pensar en nada de esto, maldita sea..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1102
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_bd39e652:

    # "Before I know it, I'm walking into the start of another school week."
    "Antes de darme cuenta estoy por comenzar otra semana de escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1103
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_94e0bae4:

    # "That weekend I just had with Hiroko... I could almost believe I imagined it, surreal as it was."
    "El fin de semana que pasé con Hiroko... me cuesta no creer que lo imaginé; fue tan surreal."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1105
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_f7983fe0:

    # "But I really did spend the whole weekend helping her with her stupid tennis tourney only for her to tell me it meant nothing."
    "Pero en verdad pasé un fin de semana entero ayudándola con su estúpido torneo de tenis, solo para que me dijera que no sirvió de nada."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1107
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_10f0f7a9:

    # t "Now class, I hope you all remember you'll be doing your mock entrance exams in a couple days."
    t "Ahora, clase, espero que todos recuerden que sus exámenes simulacro serán en un par de días."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1108
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_1e9340b9:

    # "Huh? What's our homeroom teacher saying?"
    "¿Eh? ¿Qué dijo el profesor?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1109
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_9b03498a:

    # t "While these examinations will in no way impact upon your admittance to your college of choice..."
    t "Si bien estas pruebas no impactarán de ninguna forma su admisión a la universidad de su elección..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1110
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_4c9fff99:

    # "Oh... right. I guess I was supposed to study for those."
    "Oh... cierto. Creo que se suponía que estudiara para esos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1111
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_f8b1bb85:

    # t "... It'll be your final chance to check your progress and readjust before the examinations proper, so DO take them seriously, people..."
    t "... Será su última oportunidad de evaluar su progreso y reajustarse antes de los exámenes verdaderos, así que tómenselos EN SERIO..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1113
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_691432f7:

    # "She looks as fucked off as I do. I don't think she's even talked to her friends today."
    "Luce tan jodida como yo. Creo que ni siquiera ha hablado con sus amigas hoy."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1117
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_49dbd901:

    # "As lunch rolls around once more, I lean forward a little as I watch Hiroko and her group pull themselves away from their seats."
    "Cuando llega nuevamente la hora del almuerzo, me inclino un poco hacia adelante, viendo a Hiroko y a su grupo levantarse de sus asientos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1125
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_e77c19bf:

    # n "So... Can we talk about yesterday or are you going to blow me off again?"
    n "Y... ¿podemos hablar de lo de ayer o vas a mandarme a volar otra vez?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1127
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_2b295abf:

    # h "L-Leave off, Nozo, I ain't in a talking mood..."
    h "D-déjame en paz, Nozo, no estoy de humor para hablar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1128
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_33249218:

    # n sad_closed "You didn't even come to celebrate with us. I had the room booked and everything." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Ni siquiera viniste a celebrar con nosotras. Tenía una habitación reservada y todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1129
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_1d4a266a:

    # h sleeptalk "Yeah, well I ain't in a singing mood either." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Seh, pues, tampoco estoy de humor para cantar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1130
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_4fcb1ede:

    # s uniform sleep "Nozomi, I think it best you leave her be. She will talk when she's ready." with dissolve
    s uniform sleep "Nozomi, creo que será mejor que la dejes tranquila. Hablará cuando esté lista." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1131
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_95a192c8:

    # h neutral_side "What she said. I just gotta figure some shit out." with dissolve
    h neutral_side "Lo que ella dijo. Es solo mierda con la que estoy lidiando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1132
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_fda95240:

    # n sad_side "... Sure." with dissolve
    n sad_side "... Claro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1137
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_67d1a47b:

    # "Hiroko winds up wandering out of the classroom alone while Nozomi and her other friend stay behind." with dissolve
    "Hiroko cierra la conversación saliendo del salón sola, dejando atrás a Nozomi y a su otra amiga." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1139
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_d7f421e1:

    # "I don't know what to make of that. Those three seemed unseparable for most of the time we've been in this school."
    "No sé cómo tomarme eso. Esas tres han sido inseparables desde que llegamos a esta escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1140
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_be7ca8bd:

    # "Seems weird for them to part ways now."
    "Es muy raro que ahora estén tomando caminos distintos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1149
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_f161e091:

    # "But still... This has presented me with a chance."
    "Sin embargo... Esto me da una oportunidad."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1151
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_14fc01ca:

    # "Hiroko usually lunches on the mostly deserted roof."
    "Hiroko suele almorzar en la casi desértica azotea."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1152
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_e04199ad:

    # "Her friends typically join her, but..."
    "Sus amigas normalmente la acompañan, pero..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1154
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_2981586c:

    # "Not this time. This time she's looking wistfully out over the school grounds."
    "No esta vez. Esta vez está mirando con melancolía el paisaje que rodea nuestra escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1155
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_c2f914a4:

    # "Well... If I'm going to do this, it needs to be now."
    "Bueno... si voy a hacer esto, es ahora o nunca."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1160
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_faa2bb91:

    # "No. No, I still can't do this, what the fuck am I thinking?"
    "No. No, no puedo hacerlo. ¿En qué mierda estoy pensando?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1161
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_aefc3682:

    # "If I do this... If I just up and wave my penlight in her face all I'll be doing is proving her right."
    "Si lo hago... Si voy y enciendo mi linterna en su rostro, solo le estaría dando la razón."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1162
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_5591a61a:

    # "Maybe I'll... I'll just go talk to her. Be cool about this."
    "Tal vez... tal vez sea mejor que hable con ella. Tomármelo con calma."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1164
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_3766d803:

    # "Yeah, just... go over there and stand by her side."
    "Sí, solo... iré y me pararé junto a ella."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1165
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_44305bfa:

    # "And I'll say, uh..."
    "Y diré, eh..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1167
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_241f8704:

    # h neutral "Why do you like Nozo so much?" with dissolve
    h neutral "¿Por qué Nozo te gusta tanto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1168
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_ab62fc87:

    # ks surprised "H-huh?"
    ks surprised "¿E-eh?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1169
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_9e5b370a:

    # h sleep "Just something I've been thinking about." with dissolve
    h sleep "Me lo he estado preguntando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1919
