translate spanish Day8_Redemption_dfacf417:

    # "This is what my life's going to be like from now on?"
    "¿Así será mi vida de ahora en adelante?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1982
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_bbcee925:

    # n "{size=15}K- Kyou...{/size}"
    n "{size=15}K- Kyou...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1983
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_967a500f:

    # "No one can live like this. This is..."
    "Nadie puede vivir así. Esto es..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1984
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_71846403:

    # "Wait."
    "Espera."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1987
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_b6131e0b:

    # "As I turn around, I realize I'm being followed." with dissolve
    "Me doy la vuela, y me doy cuenta de que alguien me está siguiendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1988
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_f05498b8:

    # "By..."
    "Y es..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1990
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_4f272972:

    # n sleeptalk "I..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Este..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1991
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_d9fae5ea:

    # n side sad_closed "C-can... can we talk?" with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "¿P-podemos... hablar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1996
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_03ed54d2:

    # "My heart's in my mouth."
    "Tengo el corazón en la boca."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1997
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_772fda84:

    # "Nozomi... out of everyone in the school, Nozomi wants to talk to me?"
    "Nozomi... De entre todos en la escuela, ¿Nozomi quiere hablar conmigo?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2001
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_b25b22f3:

    # "As we sit down at a nearby café, I watch as she settles in the seat opposite to me."
    "Nos sentamos en una cafetería cercana, y la miro mientras se acomoda en un asiento frente a mí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2002
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_a9839cc0:

    # "She seems so nervous. Much like she was when I last saw her up on the school rooftop."
    "Luce muy nerviosa. Tanto como la última vez que la vi allá en la azotea de la escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2360
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_8f8b8899:

    # n "Now Kyou, before we start... could I ask that you put your hands on the table, please? Where I can see them?" with dissolve
    n "Bien, Kyou, antes de que hablemos... ¿Puedo pedirte que pongas las manos sobre la mesa, por favor? ¿Donde pueda verlas?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2005
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_6dffe5c4:

    # ks surprised "Huh?"
    ks surprised "¿Eh?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2006
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_1bf14729:

    # "I do as she asks and place my hands out in front of her, palms down on the table, but I have to admit I'm a little confused."
    "Hago lo que me pide y coloco mis manos ante ella, palmas en la superficie de la mesa, pero debo admitir que estoy un poco confundido."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2012
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_8970a036:

    # n "That seems a little silly, doesn't it?" with dissolve
    n "Parece algo tonto, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2013
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_7d7e50f7:

    # ks sigh "I mean... kinda?"
    ks sigh "Pues... ¿un poco?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2015
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_1eff2f9f:

    # "Nozomi breathes a sigh as she closes her eyes, considering her next words." with dissolve
    "Nozomi suspira, cerrando los ojos para considerar sus próximas palabras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2016
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_603dd1c2:

    # "And I notice she's still trying to avoid eye contact with me."
    "Y noto que aún intenta evitar el contacto visual conmigo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2017
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_1db51d30:

    # n "Kyou, a week ago you and I were alone in the classroom together. One moment we were talking, the next there were flashes of light and then..."
    n "Kyou, hace una semana, cuando tú y yo estábamos a solas en el salón. Un instante estábamos hablando, al siguiente hubo luces y destellos, y luego..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2019
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_43646a1e:

    # n "Then I started to feel things about you that I have never felt about anyone in my entire life." with dissolve
    n "Empecé a sentir cosas sobre ti que nunca en mi vida sentí por nadie más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2021
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_3785c4ce:

    # n "Intimate... things..." with dissolve
    n "Cosas... íntimas..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2023
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_d69deb58:

    # n "I-it confused me so much. It's been like I couldn't trust my own feelings and that..." with dissolve
    n "M-me confundió mucho. Era como si no pudiera confiar en mis propios sentimientos y eso..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2025
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_514629c2:

    # n "That scared me." with dissolve
    n "Eso me asustó." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2027
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_136a1cc8:

    # n "And gosh, don't even get me started on what happened to Hiroko." with dissolve
    n "Y Dios, ni hablar de lo que le pasó a Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2028
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_a9ee2051:

    # "Yeah, I get it."
    "Sí, entiendo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2029
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_91fcb1f6:

    # "Even though she agreed to this meeting, she's still terrified of me."
    "Aunque haya accedido a esta reunión, sigue aterrada de mí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2030
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_2338fd61:

    # "Of the fact I was able to hypnotize her so easily. So completely."
    "Del hecho de que pude hipnotizarla tan fácilmente. Tan plenamente."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2031
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_2e1fa601:

    # ks sigh "Nozomi... I'm really sorry."
    ks sigh "Nozomi... En verdad lo lamento."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2033
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_384a6576:

    # n "I know, Kyou. I know." with dissolve
    n "Lo sé, Kyou. Lo sé." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2035
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_01fd47c8:

    # n "It's the only reason we're even talking." with dissolve
    n "Es la única razón por la que estamos hablando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2036
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_8665b3c1:

    # "So she accepts my apology at least? That does give me some hope."
    "Entonces, ¿al menos acepta mi disculpa? Eso me da algo de esperanza."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2038
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_b5f3fffa:

    # n "But I don't understand how you even did something like this?" with dissolve
    n "Pero no entiendo cómo lograste hacer algo así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2040
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_804165f8:

    # n "I mean, even after everything I can still feel... still feel there's something about you that's oddly relaxing..." with dissolve
    n "Es que, incluso después de todo lo que ha pasado, aún siento... siento que hay algo en ti que es extrañamente relajante..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2041
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_31bca307:

    # "Oh man, now that I think of it, with all my worry about Hiroko I never considered how my hypnosis affected Nozomi."
    "Oh, cielos, ahora que lo pienso, con toda mi preocupación por Hiroko, no me paré a pensar en cómo mi hipnosis afectó a Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2042
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_022cf909:

    # ks neutral "Right... Yeah, Nozomi, I can explain."
    ks neutral "Claro... Sí, Nozomi, puedo explicarlo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2044
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_5270e3a0:

    # "Nozomi suddenly snaps her eyes shut as she realizes she was staring right back at me." with dissolve
    "Nozomi de pronto cierra los ojos, al darse cuenta de que me estaba mirando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2045
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_07f96026:

    # "Maybe our hypnosis session was interrupted by Kobayashi, but could it be possible some of those hypnotic suggestions I gave her are still rattling around in her head?"
    "Tal vez nuestra sesión de hipnosis fue interrumpida por Kobayashi, pero ¿será posible que algunas de las sugestiones hipnóticas que le di sigan en su cabeza?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2046
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_a1585d6b:

    # ks "That light you saw. It came from a penlight that I modified to be extra eye-catching."
    ks "Esa luz que viste. Venía de una linterna que modifiqué para que llame más la atención."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2047
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_13ed9212:

    # ks "But after I used it on the two of you I had to believe it was doing so much more than encouraging you to focus."
    ks "Pero tras haberla usado en ti, creo que hace mucho más que solo ayudar a concentrarse."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2048
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_ab62dc85:

    # ks "Like, not only did you drop straight into trance whether you wanted to or not, I discovered you were taking in my every suggestion with only the tiniest resistance."
    ks "Digo, no solo entraste directo al trance, lo hayas querido o no; descubrí que estabas absorbiendo toda sugestión con la más mínima resistencia."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2049
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_2ab3cf27:

    # ks "That's why my presence relaxes you. I impressed that on you."
    ks "Es por eso que mi presencia te relaja. Yo te dije que así sería."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2051
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_95b889f0:

    # ks "And that's why Hiroko was fawning over me until I hypnotized her again and took it all back."
    ks "Y también es por eso que Hiroko me estaba adulando hasta que volví a hipnotizarla y lo deshice todo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2054
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_eb2fa6d4:

    # ks "But you have to believe I never knew what my penlight was capable of. I didn't design it for that. No one could!"
    ks "Pero tienes que creerme cuando digo que no sabía de lo que mi linterna era capaz. No la diseñé para eso. ¡Nadie podría!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2055
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_1534d572:

    # ks "I don't know if I could even make another one of these. I have no idea how I made it work like this the first time."
    ks "Ni siquiera sé si podría hacer otra igual. No tengo idea de cómo la hice funcionar así en primer lugar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2056
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_282d9551:

    # ks "And I haven't used it since, Nozomi. Not at all."
    ks "Y no la he usado desde entonces, Nozomi. Ni una vez."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2057
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_4a73ea36:

    # n "Haven't used it since..."
    n "No la has usado desde entonces..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2059
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_8e1a656c:

    # n "So you still have it?" with dissolve
    n "¿O sea que aún la tienes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2060
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_0556daad:

    # "Her question catches me off guard."
    "Su pregunta me toma desprevenido."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2061
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_70c65fa4:

    # ks sigh "I... It's not like I was going to use it like I did before. I'm never doing that again."
    ks sigh "Yo... No es como que iba a usarla como la usé antes. Nunca lo volveré a hacer."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2062
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_9daeca01:

    # n "So why keep it?"
    n "Entonces, ¿por qué conservarla?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2063
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_d1fedf63:

    # "... Why AM I keeping it?"
    "... ¿POR QUÉ aún la conservo?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2064
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_009b0b7b:

    # ks "Uhh..."
    ks "Eeeh..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2065
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_0b4d6ff5:

    # "Right here in my pocket, even."
    "Y justo aquí en mi bolsillo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2066
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_69e06b0a:

    # ks frown "Look, I know it's dangerous, but what if I could use it to help people? Don't you think that's worth exploring, Nozomi?"
    ks frown "Mira, sé que es peligrosa, pero ¿qué tal si pudiera usarla para ayudar a la gente? ¿No crees que vale la pena explorar algo así, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2068
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_cb33f82a:

    # n "Ahh..." with dissolve
    n "Aah..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2069
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_0ede8d63:

    # "Nozomi lets out a long sigh, her eyebrows twitching then relaxing, like she's not sure whether to be angry with me or not."
    "Nozomi deja salir un largo suspiro, torciendo y relajando sus cejas, como si no estuviera segura de estar enojada conmigo o no."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2070
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_097937e6:

    # n "Kyou, it's... you can't."
    n "Kyou, eso... no puedes."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2071
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_5aabbea1:

    # ks neutral "What do you mean I can't?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué quieres decir con que no puedo?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2072
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_08988a30:

    # n "Please... If that light you have is really what did that to me and Hiroko, you can't... you can't use it anymore."
    n "Por favor... Si esa linterna es realmente lo que nos hizo eso a mí y a Hiroko, no puedes... no puedes volver a usarla."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2073
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_eab29283:

    # n "If you really meant what you said up on that roof..."
    n "Si lo que dijiste en esa azotea es verdad..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2074
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_140c4f58:

    # ks sigh "I... yeah."
    ks sigh "Yo... sí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2075
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_fa7b3438:

    # "I don't want to argue with her. Not in the distress she seems to be in."
    "No quiero discutir con ella. No con la aflicción que parece estar sintiendo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2076
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_04a12103:

    # "But I need to ask her..."
    "Pero debo preguntarle..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2077
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_65d7ab3d:

    # ks neutral "So, Nozomi..."
    ks neutral "Entonces, Nozomi..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2078
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_cefdfb50:

    # ks "If I never used that penlight again, maybe even broke it... could I see you again?"
    ks "Si nunca vuelvo a usar la linterna, y tal vez hasta la destruyo... ¿podría volver a verte?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2080
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_b893beba:

    # n "Huh?!" with dissolve
    n "¡¿Eh?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2081
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_25efeb26:

    # ks "Like, here or in school, or... wherever?"
    ks "Digo, aquí o en la escuela, o... ¿en algún lado?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2083
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_ccfc9b9f:

    # n "Kyou..." with dissolve
    n "Kyou..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2084
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_f1f4dd90:

    # n "I can forgive you for what you did to me. I think you're trying to be a better person."
    n "Puedo perdonarte por lo que me hiciste a mí. Creo que intentas ser una mejor persona."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2085
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_fb0473fa:

    # n "But we can't see each other again. Not like this."
    n "Pero no podemos volver a vernos. No así."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2086
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_792023c1:

    # ks surprised "What? Nozomi, why? I can't..."
    ks surprised "¿Qué? Nozomi, ¿por qué? No puedo..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2087
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_05b125a7:

    # "And just like that I can feel what's left of my heart breaking."
    "Y así nada más, siento cómo lo poco que queda de mi corazón se hace pedazos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2088
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_87c9c269:

    # ks sigh "I can't go on like this. I need something to keep me going! Please!"
    ks sigh "No puedo continuar así. ¡Necesito algo que me haga seguir adelante! ¡Por favor!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2122
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_7b46f4ef:

    # "But Nozomi's way of response is to haul herself up from the table."
    "Pero en respuesta, Nozomi se arrastra fuera de la mesa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2123
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_f284f49f:

    # ks surprised "Nozomi!"
    ks surprised "¡Nozomi!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2124
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_30489117:

    # n "I may be able to forgive you."
    n "Tal vez yo pueda perdonarte."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2125
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_e40d8426:

    # n sleep_concerned "But Hiroko..." with dissolve
    n sleep_concerned "Pero Hiroko..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2126
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_8741d797:

    # n side sad_side "No apology is ever going to fix what happened to her, Kyou." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "No hay disculpa que pueda arreglar lo que le pasó a ella, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3673
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_d60c18f6:

    # ks confused "Because of yesterday?"
    ks confused "¿Por lo de ayer?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2128
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_22388109:

    # n sad_closed "Because she has no scholarship. That tournament was her only chance." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Porque se ha quedado sin beca. Ese torneo era su única oportunidad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2129
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_ea4d2455:

    # "\"That tournament\"?"
    "¿\"Ese torneo\"?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2130
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_74b269a5:

    # "Oh... right. There was some big sports event going on at the school this weekend. So that's what it was."
    "Oh... es cierto. Iba a haber un gran evento deportivo en la escuela el pasado fin de semana."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2131
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_00503ecc:

    # n sad "I can't betray her by associating with the person who hurt her so much." with dissolve
    n sad "No puedo traicionarla asociándome con la persona que le hizo tanto daño." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2132
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_23800bbe:

    # n sad_closed "So goodbye... And good luck." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Así que adiós... Y buena suerte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2139
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_13b14a95:

    # "So Nozomi can forgive me. Even entertain the thought of spending time with me..."
    "Conque Nozomi puede perdonarme. Incluso concebir la idea de pasar tiempo conmigo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2140
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_25b25281:

    # "But she won't, because of what I did to Hiroko. Because of how much I affected her."
    "Pero no lo hará, por lo que le hice a Hiroko. Por lo mucho que la afecté."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2141
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_01d55bba:

    # "How was I supposed to know this would happen? This isn't... this isn't fair!"
    "¿Cómo iba a saber que esto pasaría? Esto... ¡esto no es justo!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2142
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_93b779cd:

    # "And what am I supposed to do with your forgiveness, Nozomi? How does that help me?!"
    "¿Y qué se supone que haga con tu perdón, Nozomi? ¡¿Eso cómo me ayuda?!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2501
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_9650f0c5:

    # "How does that help anyone?"
    "¿Cómo ayuda a nadie?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2502
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_516d2c81:

    # "... Do I need to help Hiroko, then?"
    "... Entonces, ¿debo ayudar a Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2145
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_a76b3614:

    # "If apologizing isn't enough, then can I make an effort to help her?"
    "Si disculparme no es suficiente, ¿puedo hacer un esfuerzo por ayudarla?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2148
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_b8ced9b2:

    # "I... COULD help her. Maybe she blew her scholarship chances because of me, but at least I could ease her pain."
    "Sí... PODRÍA ayudarla. Habrá perdido la oportunidad de tener una beca por mi culpa, pero al menos podría calmar su dolor."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2149
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_99d3f5c2:

    # "Maybe I really should have done this all along. Just remove those horrid memories of me and her, then at least she could move on with her life."
    "Tal vez debí hacer esto desde el principio. Remover los horribles recuerdos que compartimos, y luego al menos podrá seguir con su vida."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2150
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_e43e0976:

    # "And sure, I know I shouldn't hypnotize my way out of my problems, but what other choice is there?"
    "Y claro, sé que la hipnosis no es la solución a todos mis problemas, pero ¿qué otra opción tengo?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2151
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_636f6078:

    # "This could be the ONLY way to make things better for everyone."
    "Puede que esta sea la única manera de que las cosas mejoren para todos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2152
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_bfacc2bc:

    # "Hiroko's suffering because of me. I know that. And for all her faults she doesn't deserve what happened to her at all."
    "Hiroko está sufriendo por mi culpa. Eso lo sé. Y a pesar de sus defectos, no se merece lo que le ocurrió."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2153
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_5fd621a4:

    # "So I'll stop her suffering. I'll heal the damage I did."
    "Así que acabaré con su sufrimiento. Sanaré el daño que hice."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2154
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_294b7924:

    # "Then Nozomi will understand, won't she?"
    "Entonces Nozomi entenderá, ¿no?"

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Kyou 8.rpy:2155
    old "Plan to hypnotize Hiroko"
    new "Hacer un plan para hipnotizar a Hiroko"

    # game/Kyou 8.rpy:2459
    old " (disabled)Plan to hypnotize Hiroko"
    new ""

    # game/Kyou 8.rpy:2155
    old "Break the penlight"
    new "Destruir la linterna"

