    # "Just to prove to everyone that I'm as much a creep as they said..."
    "Solo para probarles a todos que soy el bicho que creen que soy..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2185
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_8b95c4a2:

    # "I mean, what more proof do I need? I was even thinking to use this thing on Hiroko again. Knowing what it does..."
