    "Pero de eso siempre se trató todo esto, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2188
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_d80f90c7:

    # "I made this penlight to help me hypnotize people. A tool to make things easier for myself."
    "Hice esta pluma linterna para que me ayude a hipnotizar gente. Una herramienta para facilitarme las cosas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2189
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_901b1592:

    # "That's just me all over, isn't it. Always looking for the easy way out."
    "Así soy yo, ¿no es cierto? Siempre buscando la salida fácil."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2190
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_1bb37860:

    # "And all it ever does is get people hurt."
    "Y lo único que eso logra herir a la gente."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2191
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_bb36cca7:

    # "That's who I am..."
    "Ese soy yo..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3737
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_2dd08fbe:

    # k "I'm fucking {nw}"
    k "¡Soy un puto EN{nw}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2194
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_8b70566a:

    # extend "SICK!{w=1.0}{nw}" with shake
    extend "FERMO!{w=1.0}{nw}" with shake

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2197
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_dc3e50e7:

    # "I'm n-no good to anybody."
    "N-no le hago bien a nadie."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2198
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_9bb6069a:

    # "Why did I ever think I could make things better?"
    "¿Por qué pensé que podría mejorar las cosas?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2200
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_2c32c944:

    # "What could I possibly do to help anyone...?"
    "¿Que podría hacer yo para ayudar a nadie…?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2201
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_0cee695e:

    # "Have I even thought about it at all?"
    "¿Siquiera me he puesto a pensarlo?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2202
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_b298888d:

    # "They said Hiroko crashed out of her tennis tourney and that's why she's going to fail to get the scholarship she needs."
    "Dijeron que Hiroko arruinó su torneo de tenis, y por eso no obtendrá la beca que necesita."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2203
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_a4af48c9:

    # "How was hypnotizing her again going to fix any of that?"
    "¿Cómo hipnotizarla de nuevo arreglaría eso?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2204
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_53d7bfa9:

    # "What could I even do to help her in that kind of situation?"
    "¿Qué puedo hacer yo para ayudarla en esa clase de situación?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2213
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_a2c4dbd0:

    # "... First I'd have to think about why she crashed out."
    "... Primero tendría que pensar en por qué lo arruinó."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2214
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_bf0dddb0:

    # "Most likely because she was still in a bad way over what I did to her a week ago."
    "Probablemente porque aún se sentía mal por lo que le hice hace una semana."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2215
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_3b5f9dc6:

    # "She was in no shape to be evaluated for anything, let alone something that was going to make or break her career."
    "No estaba en condiciones de ser evaluada para nada, mucho menos algo que fuera de vida o muerte para su carrera."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2216
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_f4870d3c:

    # "If she was in as bad a way as Risa and Nozomi said, surely anyone else could have seen that."
    "Si estaba tan mal como Risa y Nozomi dijeron, seguramente todos pudieron verlo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2217
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_944288de:

    # "And who said it was Hiroko's last chance at a scholarship? Just them?"
    "¿Y quién dijo que era la última oportunidad de Hiroko de conseguir una beca? ¿Solo ellas?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2218
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_d9e82f4f:

    # "... What if it wasn't?"
    "... ¿Qué tal si no lo fuera?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2078
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_67e29e4b:

    # ks "And that's why Hiroko legit thought she was some kind of robot until I hypnotized her again and took it all back."
    ks "Y también es por eso que Hiroko se creía alguna clase de robot hasta que volví a hipnotizarla y lo deshice todo."

