    # scg drooping alert_sleeptalk "After the ordeal I just had, to be able to share my time with you once more, even in this circumstance, is the sweetest relief." with dissolve
    scg drooping alert_sleeptalk "Tras el suplicio que acabo de pasar, poder compartir mi tiempo contigo una vez más, a pesar de las circunstancias, es el más dulce alivio." with dissolve
