# game/Kyou 8.rpy:727
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_767384eb:

    # "The only reason [alt_name] exists is because I was selfish and reckless with a person who trusted me more than I deserved. I can admit it."
    "La única razón por la que [alt_name] existe es que fui egoísta e insensato con una persona que confío en mí más de lo que merecía. Eso puedo admitirlo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:728
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_22523593:

    # "And yet, that's not what's important right now. The only thing that matters is that [alt_name] exists now. She lives."
    "Sin embargo, eso no es lo importante ahora. Lo único que importa es que [alt_name] existe. Esta viva."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:729
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_8ee4de2b:

    # "So Sayori, I'm sorry for everything I'm putting you through. I truly am."
    "Así que, Sayori, lamento todo por lo que te estoy haciendo pasar. En serio lo lamento."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:730
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_954eff31:

    # "But you get it, don't you?"
    "Pero tú lo entiendes, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:731
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_78de3713:

    # "Because as wrong as it was of me to bring [alt_name] into this world, taking her out of it would be even more terrible."
    "Pues por malo que haya sido traer a [alt_name] a este mundo, acabar con ella sería por mucho más terrible."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:732
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_d04abd45:

    # "I need to do my best for both of you."
    "Debo hacer lo mejor que pueda por ambas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:733
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_e6a0c9a5:

    # ks "Now I want to talk to you about [alt_name]. The happy, carefree, fun-loving woman I described to you before."
    ks "Ahora quiero hablarte de, [alt_name]. La alegre y despreocupada mujer amante de la diversión que te describí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:734
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_138c6bff:

    # ks "She exists in your mind, doesn't she, Sayori?"
    ks "Ella existe en tu mente, ¿no es cierto, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:737
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_99345f62:

    # s "... Uh-huh." with dissolve
    s "... Ajá." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:672
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_16bc6ef6:

    # ns scared "{size=16}Kyou? What are you doing?{/size}" with dissolve
    ns scared "{size=16}¿Kyou? ¿Qué estás haciendo?{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:740
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_87eb4420:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori. [alt_name] is a part of you now, and she always will be."
    ks "Así es, Sayori. [alt_name] es ahora parte de ti, y siempre lo será."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:674
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_54a5c2be:

    # ns concerned "{size=16}Kyou...{/size}"
    ns concerned "{size=16}Kyou...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:743
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_32c271d9:

    # ks "There will be times when [alt_name] will want to express herself, both to you and to other people. There'll be times when she'll want the use of the body you two share."
    ks "Habrá momentos en los que [alt_name] querrá comunicarse, tanto contigo como con otras personas. Habrá momentos en los que querrá usar el cuerpo que las dos comparten."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:677
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_1c40b15e:

    # ks "As I said, your body and mind are always yours; you're the one most in control. You'll always be exactly the person you are now."
    ks "Como dije, tu cuerpo y tu mente serán siempre tuyos; tú eres quien tiene mayor control. Siempre serás exactamente la persona que eres ahora."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:747
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_e9c78252:

    # ks "But you'll allow [alt_name] the use of your mind and body that she needs to live a life of her own."
    ks "Pero le otorgarás a [alt_name] el uso de tu mente y cuerpo que necesita para vivir su propia vida."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:749
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_efded967:

    # ks "Do you... do you understand, Sayori?"
    ks "¿Co-... comprendes, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:751
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c3e0817c:

    # s "Uh... uh-huh..." with dissolve
    s "A-... ajá..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:753
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_44466f38:

    # ks "That's great, Sayori. Because right now I need to speak to [alt_name] and tell her what I told you..." with dissolve
    ks "Grandioso, Sayori. Porque ahora necesito hablar con [alt_name] y decirle lo que te acabo de decir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:756
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_47d74c27:

    # "So... I did it. I made sure that both Sayori and [alt_name] could work as one."
    "Y... eso hice. Me aseguré de que tanto Sayori como [alt_name] pudieran vivir como una."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:757
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_34a626cc:

    # "This is the best I could do..."
    "Es lo mejor que puedo hacer..."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Kyou 8.rpy:725
    old "I won't leave you behind (Incomplete)"
    new "No pienso dejarte atrás (Incompleto)"
