# game/Kyou 8.rpy:742
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_d6dc925a:

    # ks "While your body and mind will always be yours, you must also accept that it's not yours alone."
    ks " Si bien tu cuerpo y tu mente siempre serán tuyos, debes también aceptar que no son solo tuyos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2583
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b2689d37:

    # "The next day comes and goes before I brace myself for the start of another school week."
    "El día siguiente viene y se va, y antes de darme cuenta empiezo otra semana de escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2584
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ce3b053a:

    # "My first full week as a member of class 3-C..."
    "Mi primera semana completa como miembreo de la clase 3-C..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2587
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_cd298e1e:

    # "Akiko may have lifted my spirits before, but I know she's going to be so much busier now."
    "Akiko me habrá alzado el espíritu el otro día, pero sé que ahora estará mucho más ocupada."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2588
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_41ee42e3:

    # "I'll just have to get through these days by myself..."
    "Tendré que sobrevivir estos días por mi cuenta..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2591
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f5d4d383:

    # "The best thing I can say about this week, is that it's going to be boring."
    "Lo mejor que puedo decir de esta semana es que será aburrida."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2592
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3b117ba9:

    # "Even for those of us who aren't mired in culture festival crap, we've got our mock exams to prepare for."
    "Incluso para aquellos que no estamos involucrados con esa mierda del festival cultural; tenemos exámenes simulacro para los que prepararnos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2593
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_1fbb7690:

    # "So if I just enter the classroom quietly and take my seat by the side wall without a fuss, all I'll have to do is endure the tedium."
    "Así que, si entro en silencio al salón y tomo mi asiento junto a la pared sin causar alboroto, lo único que tendré que hacer es soportar este tedio."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3787
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_cfc72db4:

    # ks confused "I... what?"
    ks confused "Me... ¿qué?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2601
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_0bd286a7:

    # r uniform_armup "You heard me, creep. What, did you think we'd stay quiet? You think we're afraid of you?" with dissolve
    r uniform_armup "Ya me oíste, bicho raro. ¿Qué? ¿Creíste que mantendríamos la boca cerrada? ¿Crees que te tenemos miedo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2602
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3862d163:

    # ks "I don't..."
    ks "No..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2603
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f41806d1:

    # r uniform angry "We KNOW what you did to Hiroko, you skeevy son of a bitch!" with dissolve
    r uniform angry "¡SABEMOS lo que le hiciste a Hiroko, asqueroso hijo de perra!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2604
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4222f0ea:

    # "What I did... to..."
    "Lo que... le hice a..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2605
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e7fcf0d3:

    # r uniform_armup "Well? You got anything to say for yourself?" with dissolve
    r uniform_armup "¿Y bien? ¿Qué tienes que decir en tu defensa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2606
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ce380fa2:

    # "What AM I supposed to say to this? Did Hiroko run her mouth off to these people, or..."
    "¿Y QUÉ se supone que diga? ¿Hiroko les contó todo a estas personas, o...?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2607
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_52ce70a3:

    # "I don't know. What do they think I've done THIS time?"
    "No sé. ¿Qué es lo que creen que hice ESTA vez?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2608
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_658c195c:

    # ks sigh "I haven't even gone near any of you. Just leave me alone."
    ks sigh "Ni siquiera me les he acercado. Ya déjenme en paz."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2612
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_0258d29d:

    # a "Good morning, everyone!" with dissolve
    a "¡Buenos días a todos!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2614
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f11ce737:

    # "Maybe she can talk some sense into these people."
    "Tal vez ella pueda hacer a esta gente entrar en razón."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2617
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_44afc6d6:

    # r "And YOU! I don't know how you can live with yourself." with dissolve
    r "¡Y TÚ! No sé cómo puedes vivir contigo misma." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2618
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_5d9feabb:

    # "But it seems Risa has it out for her as well, somehow. Is she always like this?"
    "Pero parece que Risa también está furiosa con ella, de alguna forma. ¿Siempre actúa así?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2620
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_9efff49b:

    # r uniform frown_side "Your little psych patient is why Hiroko crashed and burned yesterday. But you knew that, didn't you." with dissolve
    r uniform frown_side "Tu disque-paciente psiquiátrico este es la razón por la que Hiroko salió hecha un desastre ayer. Pero tú ya lo sabías, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2621
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a983f864:

    # "... What's she talking about? Yesterday?"
    "... ¿De qué está hablando? ¿Ayer?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2623
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d5ac5cf7:

    # "What happened yesterday?"
    "¿Qué sucedió ayer?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2624
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_6f3f1acd:

    # r angry_side "You were there. You SAW her and... Jesus, why do you keep sticking your neck out for this guy?" with dissolve
    r angry_side "Estabas ahí. Tú la VISTE y... Por Dios, ¿por qué sigues defendiendo a este chico?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2625
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_fbb08dfd:

    # a frown_side "Because I don't listen to rumours and innuendo. I'll form my own opinion." with dissolve
    a frown_side "Porque yo no escucho los rumores e insinuaciones. Formo una opinión propia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2626
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a7fc666a:

    # a angry_side "Especially when the rumours are all so STUPID!" with dissolve
    a angry_side "¡Sobre todo cuando los rumores son tan ESTÚPIDOS!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2627
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_136c7938:

    # "Akiko gestures wildly to the rest of the class, while I'm still trying to figure out what even happened."
    "Akiko le hace un gran gesto al resto de la clase, mientras que yo aún intento averiguar qué fue lo que pasó."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2629
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_bf4a7945:

    # a angry "You can't make someone do anything they don't want to with hypnosis. And that's a rock-solid FACT!" with dissolve
    a angry "No puedes obligar a alguien a hacer nada que no quiera hacer con hipnosis. ¡Y eso es un HECHO grabado a fuego!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2630
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d4ffe7cf:

    # "I mean... yeah, Akiko, you're right, but..."
    "Bueno... sí, Akiko, tienes razón, pero..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2633
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_588ffd6e:

    # a "So if she found herself going along with whatever he told her, assuming she was hypnotized at all, what do you think that tells us, Risa?" with dissolve
    a "Así que si ella le estaba siguiendo la corriente a lo que sea que le dijo, asumiendo que siquiera estaba hipnotizada para empezar, ¿qué crees que eso nos dice, Risa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2634
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_87b55588:

    # r uniform_armup angry_side "Are you for REAL?!" with dissolve
    r uniform_armup angry_side "¡¿Hablas en SERIO?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2635
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_7d8b0ff2:

    # "I mean, it IS the penlight they're really talking about here, even if they don't realize it..."
    "Bueno, de lo que están hablando realmente es la linterna, incluso si no se dan cuenta..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2636
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a4b9c23c:

    # r uniform frown "He hurt her, 'Kiko. That's why they moved him in here with us. The whole school knows it." with dissolve
    r uniform frown "Le hizo daño, 'Kiko. Por eso lo movieron aquí con nosotros. Toda la escuela lo sabe." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2637
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_fdebda55:

    # r frown_side "Everyone except you. You just have to find the deeper meaning behind everything; like you know better than us." with dissolve
    r frown_side "Todos excepto tú. Tú tienes que estarle buscando el significado oculto a todo; como si fueras más lista que nosotros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2639
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_1ee23a0c:

    # a frown_side "Besides, he's already been punished; that's why he's here with us." with dissolve
    a frown_side "Además, él ya fue castigado; por eso está aquí con nosotros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2640
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_0350a6f3:

    # r angry_side "You call this a punishment? The prick didn't even get detention." with dissolve
    r angry_side "¿A esto le llamas castigo? El cabrón ni siquiera fue a detención." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2641
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a6e7309c:

    # r frown "All they did was set him loose on us, and now he knows he can harass us all he wants and no one will do shit about it!" with dissolve
    r frown "¡Lo único que hicieron fue soltárnoslo a nosotros, y ahora sabemos que puede acosarnos todo lo que quiera y nadie hará una mierda al respecto!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2643
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f39f5c93:

    # a neutral_side "Look... I'm sorry about what happened to Hiroko. I know Kyou did something foolish and he really should have known better." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Mira... Lamento lo que le pasó a Hiroko. Sé que Kyou hizo algo tonto y realmente debió haber sido más sensato." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2644
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4a67263d:

    # a sad_side "My heart goes out to her, and I hope she can find the help she needs, but this? Risa, this isn't helping her at all." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Mi corazón está con ella, y espero que encuentre la ayuda que necesita, ¿pero esto? Risa, esto no ayuda en nada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2645
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_308b225e:

    # r uniform_armup angry "It'll help everyone if we show our school we won't tolerate a harrassing creep in our classrooms." with dissolve
    r uniform_armup angry "Ayudará a todos si le mostramos a la escuela que no toleraremos a un bicho raro acosador en nuestros salones." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2654
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_c1ea761d:

    # a frown_side "By clinging to rumours and pointing fingers?" with dissolve
    a frown_side "¿Creando rumores y acusaciones?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2659
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_41590ac7:

    # r angry_side "Y-you..." with dissolve
    r angry_side "E-eres una..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2660
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_339a89ad:

    # t "{cps=15}Good morning, class-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    t "{cps=15}Buenos días, cla-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2667
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e6acd319:

    # r "How DARE you!" with vpunch
    r "¡¿Cómo te ATREVES?!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2687
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_13059093:

    # "... It almost feels like time stands still, as the sound of Risa's hand striking Akiko's cheek seems to ring out around the classroom."
    "... Casi parece que el tiempo se detiene cuando el sonido de la mano de Risa azotando la mejilla de Akiko resuena en el aula de clases."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2690
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3023a183:

    # "Until at last I spy our homeroom teacher beginning to thrust a finger in Risa's direction, almost appearing to move in slow-motion."
    "Hasta que, finalmente, veo a nuestra profesora alzar un dedo en dirección a Risa, casi pareciendo moverse en cámara lenta."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2693
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_fe536948:

    # t "Principal's office. NOW!"
    t "Oficina del director. ¡AHORA!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2697
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_1ccb287b:

    # r "Y-yes, ma'am..."
    r "S-sí, señora..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2699
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_c4dd5c22:

    # "... before walking quietly to leave. It's only when she slides the door open that anyone dares break the silence."
    "... para después caminar a la salida sin decir una palabra. No es hasta que desliza la puerta que alguien se atreve a romper el silencio."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2702
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b2b961c6:

    # a sad_side "{cps=20}I could go with her. Explain to the principal- {/cps}{w=1.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    a sad_side "{cps=20}Podría ir con ella. Explicarle al director- {/cps}{w=1.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2703
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_997fbde2:

    # t "Take your seat, Tsushima."
    t "Tome asiento, Tsushima."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2705
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_82eba9b5:

    # "I can see Akiko tense as she stands in front of my desk. I guess she probably wants to say something more about what went down." with dissolve
    "Puedo ver a Akiko ponerse tensa frente a mi escritorio. Seguro quiere decir algo más sobre lo que ocurrió." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2706
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_6b1a9430:

    # a uniform_down armband_down "... Yes, Ms. Chiba." with dissolve
    a uniform_down armband_down "... Sí, Profesora Chiba." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2708
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4d75c1a2:

    # "But our homeroom teacher's obviously more concerned about bringing order back to her classroom, and Akiko keeps the rest to herself as she returns to her desk."
    "Pero a nuestra profesora obviamente le preocupa más reestablecer el orden en su salón, y Akiko se guarda el resto, regresando a su escritorio."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2710
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f4d86830:

    # "After that class continues for a while, almost as if nothing happened."
    "Después de eso la clase continúa por un rato, casi como si nada hubiera pasado."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2712
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e701e149:

    # "Although as the school bell rings for the start of lunch it's hard not to notice that Risa didn't come back."
    "Aunque cuando la campana suena, anunciando el inicio del almuerzo, es difícil no notar que Risa no regresa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2719
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_afa1aab6:

    # "At the stroke of the bell, Akiko rises from her desk and makes a beeline for the exit while keeping her eyes to the ground."
    "Ante el azote del timbre, Akiko se levanta de su escritorio y camina en línea recta a la puerta con la mirada en el suelo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2722
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_aae96dbd:

    # "For my part, I do my best to stick to the original plan."
    "Por mi parte, hago mi mayor esfuerzo por aferrarme al plan original."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2723
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_9772b478:

    # "Keep my head down, do the work and try to ignore everything else around me."
    "Agacho la cabeza, hago el trabajo e intento ignorar todo lo demás a mi alrededor."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2725
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_de5f85dc:

    # "They hate me here. They all do..."
    "Me odian. Todos me odian..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2727
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_8f10d4d9:

    # "When we're dismissed for the day I can't get out of there fast enough."
    "Cuando nos dan permiso de retirarnos, estoy impaciente por largarme de ahí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2728
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3ff62475:

    # "I don't know how I'm gonna get through the next four days if things are going to be this tense..."
    "No sé cómo sobreviviré los próximos cuatro días si las cosas estarán así de tensas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2731
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_8623bd84:

    # "And after that?"
    "¿Y después de eso?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2733
