    # "Well, no one besides Akiko, anyway. And as she strolls into the classroom she's the person who looks the least upset around here."
    "Bueno, a nadie además de Akiko, al menos. Y al entrar al salón, ella parece la persona que está menos molesta del lugar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4079
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4743ad9a:

    # a angry_side "No Risa, if there's anyone doing any harassment around here it's you!" with dissolve
    a angry_side "¡No Risa, si alguien aquí es culpable de acoso, esa eres tú!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2720
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_20e37936:

    # "No doubt she's got student council business to occupy her, but I sure want to know what's going through that mind of hers right now..."
