    # ks "And it's... it's like you said, I didn't do anything so bad as to get suspended from school."
    ks "Y es... es como dijiste, no hice nada tan malo como para que me suspendieran de la escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2823
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_5c424711:

    # ks "Hiroko's got a right to be angry with me, and scared, and... everything else she's feeling, but I promise you I've learned from my mistakes. I've changed."
    ks "Hiroko tiene derecho a estar molesta conmigo, y asustada y... todo lo que esté sintiendo, pero te prometo que aprendí de mis errores. He cambiado."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2824
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_054dc036:

    # a sad_side "*sniffle* H-have you? How would I even know?" with dissolve
    a sad_side "*snif* ¿E-es eso cierto? ¿Cómo lo sabría?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2825
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_cf9db72b:

    # ks neutral "I... I guess you don't. But that's just it; you gave me a chance anyway. You've had faith in me since the day we met."
    ks neutral "Su-... supongo que no lo sabes. Pero ahí está la cosa; me diste una oportunidad, aun así. Tuviste fe en mí desde el día en que nos conocimos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2826
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_0ed66bd6:

    # ks "And you make me want to prove myself worthy of your faith, Akiko."
    ks "Y me haces querer demostrar que soy digno de tu fe."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2828
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d1c954c0:

    # ks "So you're not a bad person. Don't ever say that about yourself." with dissolve
    ks "Así que no eres una mala persona. Jamás digas eso de ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2829
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3970f8be:

    # a uniform armband "I... I really need to believe that, Koyama. About you and me." with dissolve
    a uniform armband "En... en serio necesito creer eso, Koyama. Sobre ti y sobre mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2831
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_01e1f0ce:

    # a sleep "So for the time being, let's just say I do." with dissolve
    a sleep "Así que, por ahora, digamos que lo creo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2832
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_5b9bd6b9:

    # "For better or worse, Akiko and I are in this mess together. And it's already starting to feel like this week is going to be the longest in our lives."
    "Para bien o para mal, Akiko y yo estamos en este desastre juntos. Y ya empiezo a sentir que esta semana será la más larga de nuestras vidas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2833
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_1abd5863:

    # "But maybe, while we're together, we can at least make a little light for ourselves..."
    "Pero tal vez, mientras estemos juntos, podamos al menos crear un poquito de luz para nosotros..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2836
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_be655eea:

    # ks "Okay. So I guess there's nothing more you can do about the student council situation until tomorrow, right?" with dissolve
    ks "Bien. Pues supongo que no hay nada más que puedas hacer respecto al consejo estudiantil hasta mañana, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2837
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d26f7cf8:

    # a neutral_side "Yup..." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Sipi..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2838
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ec5fadbd:

    # ks "So do you think it'd help to take your mind off of it for a while? Try to feel better about yourself?"
    ks "Entonces, ¿crees que pueda ayudar a sacártelo de la mente por un rato? ¿Intentar sentirte mejor contigo misma?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2840
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d1d1114a:

    # "Akiko offers a weary nod in response." with dissolve
    "Akiko asiente fatigada en respuesta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2841
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_11847b9a:

    # a sleeptalk "I was just thinking about going home, actually. Go run a nice hot bath and finish my book." with dissolve
    a sleeptalk "Tenía pensado irme a casa, de hecho. Tomar un agradable baño caliente y terminar mi libro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2842
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_422beff6:

    # a neutral_side "Losing myself in a fantasy world sounds nice right about now." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Perderme en un mundo de fantasía suena genial ahora mismo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2843
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3e9643b2:

    # a neutral "Why, did you want to hypnotize me again?" with dissolve
    a neutral "¿Por qué? ¿Querías hipnotizarme otra vez?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2844
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4b7b00ed:

    # "Yeah, she saw right through me. It's not like I've given her any reason to think I'd suggest anything else."
    "Sí, me leyó como un libro. No es que le haya dado razón para pensar que sugeriría alguna otra cosa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2845
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_69e5da24:

    # "But I don't think she's hostile to the idea. She just doesn't seem to have the energy to care at all. That might actually be worse."
    "Pero no creo que la repela la idea. Simplemente no parece tener la energía para darle importancia. Puede que eso sea peor."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2846
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4b57d4b8:

    # ks sigh "Y-yeah. I just want to make you feel better, and it worked really well the last time, so..."
    ks sigh "S-sí. Es que quiero hacerte sentir mejor, y funcionó muy bien la última vez, así que..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2849
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_7a2c5c24:

    # "As I confirm my intention she listlessly goes to sit down on my couch."
    "Tras confirmar mis intenciones, se sienta apáticamente en mi sofá."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2850
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ea63f230:

    # a "It did. But now I can't help thinking about how hypnotizing your classmates is the whole reason we're in this mess."
    a "Es cierto. Pero ahora no puedo evitar pensar en cómo hipnotizar a tus compañeras es la razón por la que estamos en este desastre en primer lugar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2852
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e73f52a0:

    # a "So maybe I shouldn't enable you like this for both our sakes." with dissolve
    a "Así que tal vez no debería estar permitiéndotelo por el bien de ambos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2853
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f72ecbca:

    # "... Okay, maybe she IS a little hostile to the idea. Wasn't expecting that after how well it went before."
    "... De acuerdo, tal vez la idea SÍ la repele un poco. No me esperaba eso luego de lo bien que salió antes."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2854
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_15e48695:

    # "But I guess today really did a number on her."
    "Pero supongo que el día de hoy sí la afectó bastante."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2856
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_dce013be:

    # ks sigh "It's not the same, Akiko. Really!"
    ks sigh "No es lo mismo, Akiko. ¡En serio!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2857
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_cfe9a2ec:

    # ks "I suggested something that made my old classmates uncomfortable and they weren't expecting it. But like I said, I've learned. I won't ever do that again."
    ks "Hice sugestiones que incomodaron a mis antiguas compañeras y no se lo esperaban. Pero como dije, he aprendido. No volveré a hacer eso."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2858
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_397838c6:

    # a "So tell me what we're doing. What should I expect?"
    a "Entonces dime qué es lo que haremos. ¿Qué debería esperar?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2859
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_8e571f92:

    # "Okay... she still wants to give me a chance. She just wants to make sure I meant what I said. Show her I really DID learn."
    "Muy bien... todavía quiere darme una oportunidad. Solo quiere asegurarse de que lo que dije era en serio. Mostrarle que SÍ aprendí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2860
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b756d0cb:

    # "I can still do this."
    "Aún puedo hacer esto."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2861
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b280a420:

    # ks neutral "Alright, so I want to try hypnotizing you with a spiral again."
    ks neutral "Muy bien, pues quiero intentar hipnotizarte con una espiral otra vez."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2862
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d4a877bb:

    # ks "And while I'm doing it, I'm going to suggest a lot of positive things to your subconscious to help you feel better."
    ks "Y mientras hago eso, le diré muchas cosas positivas a tu subconsciente para ayudarte a sentirte mejor."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2863
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e4f24a8b:

    # ks "So... I'd encourage you to smile, laugh, feel a general sense of happiness and let you push the bad feelings of the day to the back of your mind. Stuff like that."
    ks "Así que... te animaré a que sonrías, te rías, tengas una gran sensación de felicidad y empujes esos sentimientos negativos del día al fondo de tu mente. Cosas así."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2865
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_c6b4585e:

    # a "Ugh, I really don't feel like there's anything to be happy about right now." with dissolve
    a "Aj, de verdad no siento que haya nada de lo que estar feliz en este momento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2867
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ae855283:

    # a "And do you really need that silly spiral? It feels like you're mocking me with it." with dissolve
    a "¿Y en serio necesitas esa boba espiral? Ya parece que te estás burlando de mí con ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2868
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b7fd53ac:

    # ks surprised "I-I'm not mocking you with it! Really! It just worked really well the last time, that's all."
    ks surprised "¡N-no me estoy burlando de ti! ¡En serio! Es que funcionó muy bien la última vez, es todo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2869
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_5c4e47a8:

    # "Plus I don't know if I can hypnotize you any other way besides with my penlight."
    "Además no sé si pueda hipnotizarte con algún otro método que no sea mi linterna."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2870
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_44842217:

    # ks neutral "It's like I said before: There's already a strong association in your mind between seeing a spiral and becoming hypnotized."
    ks neutral "Como dije: Ya hay una gran asociación en tu mente entre ver espirales y caer hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2871
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d15ff6f8:

    # ks "And I don't think either of us have the patience to try out any new kinds of hypnotic inductions today. We should go with something we know works for you."
    ks "Y no creo que ninguno de los dos tenga la paciencia para intentar nuevos tipos de inducciones hipnóticas hoy. Deberíamos usar algo que ya sabemos que te funciona."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2872
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_56179761:

    # a "Yeah. That does make sense, I admit."
    a "Seh. Eso tiene sentido, he de admitir."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2873
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_77384d14:

    # ks smile "And I really want to try and take the edge off of today for you, Akiko. Just a little bit."
    ks smile "Y de verdad quiero intentar quitarte el peso de hoy de encima, Akiko. Aunque sea un poco."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2875
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4039bbd0:

    # ks "So... would you like me to try?"
    ks "Así que... ¿te parece si lo intento?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2877
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_38cd1a43:

    # "There's another weary sigh as Akiko tiredly nods her consent." with dissolve
    "Con otro exhausto suspiro, Akiko da su consentimiento asintiendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2879
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_61907346:

    # a "Okay. I guess that bath can wait a little longer." with dissolve
    a "Está bien. Supongo que ese baño puede esperar un poco más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2881
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_09a157ea:

    # a "{cps=20}But I really don't know if it'll work this t...{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    a "{cps=20}Pero en serio no sé si funcionará esta v...{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2884
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b972a55d:

    # extend " t-time?"
    extend " ¿v-vez?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2886
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e4871bef:

    # "The moment she agreed, I quickly went to open the spiral app I had saved on my phone and put it in front of her."
    "En cuanto dio su visto bueno, abrí rápidamente la aplicación de la espiral que tenía guardada en mi teléfono y la puse frente a ella."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2887
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_1b9fbfdd:

    # "Her reaction was almost immediate."
    "Su reacción fue casi inmediata."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2888
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_cbe38d4e:

    # ks "It'll work if you want it to, Akiko."
    ks "Funcionará si así lo quieres, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2889
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ec7b4086:

    # ks "It's been a couple of days since you've last seen this, but if you want it to draw you in... If you want it to capture all of your focused attention..."
    ks "Han pasado un par de días desde la última vez que viste esto, pero si quieres que te guíe... Si quieres que capture toda tu atención..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2890
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_23d8abf4:

    # ks "... If you want it to hypnotize you, then it will absolutely do all of those things."
    ks "... Si quieres que te hipnotice, entonces absolutamente hará todas esas cosas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2891
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_667cec3e:

    # ks "Every bit as naturally, every bit as easily as before."
    ks "De forma tan natural, tan sencilla como antes."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2901
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_bb8e4b4e:

    # a "..."
    a "..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2902
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e14f1255:

    # ks "So with all that in mind, I'd like you to just watch this for a little while. Just a little while, Akiko."
    ks "Y con todo eso en mente, quiero que observes esto por un rato. Solo un ratito, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2903
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a7361ff5:

    # ks "Just watching the spiral, and listening to my voice, and knowing that whatever happens next is up to you..."
    ks "Solo observa la espiral y escucha mi voz, y sabrás que lo que sea que pase después depende de ti..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2904
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_6f81dca0:

    # ks "Watching and listening... and listening and watching..."
    ks "Observa y escucha... y escucha y observa..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2905
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b12e6ed5:

    # ks "So now that you've been watching for a little while Akiko, I want to ask you..."
    ks "Y ahora que estuviste un rato observando, Akiko, quiero preguntar..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2906
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_df8be303:

    # ks "Do you feel yourself becoming hypnotized right now?"
    ks "¿Sientes que estás quedando hipnotizada?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2909
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_6ccb08d1:

    # a "Y... yeah, I think so..."
    a "S... sí, creo que sí..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2910
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_904b2f4b:

    # ks "Do you find the spiral hypnotic?"
    ks "¿La espiral te parece hipnótica?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2911
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_894e7159:

    # a "Yes..."
    a "Sí..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2912
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a6cfea4d:

    # "Pushing the phone just a little closer towards her face, I ask her one last important question:"
    "Acercando el teléfono ligeramente a su rostro, le hago una última pregunta:"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2913
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f600ab78:

    # ks "Do you want to be hypnotized by the spiral, Akiko?"
    ks "¿Quieres ser hipnotizada por la espiral, Akiko?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2914
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a3b6fe4f:

    # "I watch as her breath catches, while the lids of her moistened eyes twitch frantically yet never threaten to close before the ever-swirling spiral that fills her vision."
    "La veo contener el aliento. Sus húmedos párpados se contraen frenéticamente, amenazando con cerrarse ante la atrapante espiral que llena su visión."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2915
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_894e7159_1:

    # a "Yes..."
    a "Sí..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2916
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_8125b824:

    # ks "That's wonderful, Akiko. You may already be feeling very deeply hypnotized, already returning quickly to that nice pleasant state of trance."
    ks "Maravilloso, Akiko. Tal vez ya te sientas profundamente hipnotizada, volviendo rápidamente a ese placentero estado de trance."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2917
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_652089e5:

    # a "N-hnn..."
    a "N-hnn..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2918
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_652a5d0a:

    # ks "So allow yourself to go even deeper, Akiko. You can do that."
    ks "Así que déjate caer más profundo, Akiko. Puedes hacerlo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2919
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_27d59400:

    # ks "Breathe in... breathe out... letting your gaze go deeper into the hypnotic spiral. Letting yourself become completely hypnotized..."
    ks "Inhala... exhala... deja que tu mirada se adentre más profundo a la hipnótica espiral. Quedando completamente hipnotizada..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2920
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_0366dfbe:

    # ks "In three. {w=1.0}Two. {w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks "En tres. {w=1.0}Dos. {w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2923
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3e0edaca:

    # extend "One..."
    extend "Uno..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2924
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ecdac1e5:

    # "And just like that, whatever vestiges of doubt that Akiko seemed to have are wiped out as she loses herself completely in my \"silly spiral\"."
    "Y así, cualquier vestigio de duda que Akiko tuviera desaparece al perderse en mi \"boba espiral\"."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2926
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_db421589:

    # ks neutral "That's right, Akiko. Completely hypnotized. Going even deeper into the spiral. Even deeper into a pleasant, hypnotic trance..." with dissolve
    ks neutral "Eso es, Akiko. Completamente hipnotizada. Cayendo aún más profundo en la espiral. Aún más profundo en un placentero trance hipnótico..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2927
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f3f3b479:

    # "It makes me feel confident that I really can convince her to feel as good about herself as she deserves."
    "Me hace confiar en que sí puedo convencerla de sentirse bien consigo misma como merece."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2928
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4fc65492:

    # ks "And as you stare so very deeply, I want you to imagine all of your stress from today start to seep out of you."
    ks "Y al observar tan profundamente, quiero que imagines cómo todo tu estrés del día de hoy comienza a drenarse."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2930
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_9c7b2208:

    # ks "I want you to imagine it leaving your head and draining out into this spiral before you."
    ks "Quiero que lo imagines saliendo de tu cabeza y siendo absorbido por esta espiral que hay frente a ti."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2931
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_786aba74:

    # ks "Can you do that, Akiko?"
    ks "¿Puedes hacer eso, Akiko?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2933
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_7756caf3:

    # a "Yes..." with dissolve
    a "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2936
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_6263f0ae:

    # ks "And when you feel that last bit of stress has been carried away by the spiral... I want you to close your eyes."
    ks "Y cuando sientas que la última gota de estrés haya sido absorbida por la espiral... quiero que cierres los ojos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2937
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d27f82fa:

    # ks "Just letting it all out... and out..."
    ks "Deja que todo salga... que salga..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2938
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_693f818c:

    # ks "And... {w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks "Y... {w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2941
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b9c9611b:

    # extend "{w=1.0}out. Very good."
    extend "{w=1.0}salga. Muy bien."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2943
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4f13a61f:

    # "Akiko exhales gently as her eyes fall closed. So far so good." with dissolve
    "Akiko exhala suavemente y sus ojos se cierran. De momento, todo va bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2944
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_7750d2e0:

    # "But now I want her to feel better than she could ever get from that bath she was planning."
    "Pero ahora quiero que se sienta mejor de lo que jamás habría podido con ese baño que planeaba."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2945
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_10881bd1:

    # ks "Feeling so free from stress... but I can make you feel even better, Akiko. I can take this relaxed, stress-free feeling you're experiencing and take it even further."
    ks "Se siente muy bien estar libre de estrés... pero puedo hacerte sentir aún mejor, Akiko. Tomar esta sensación que estás experimentarlo y llevarla más allá."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2946
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3e524850:

    # ks "I can make you as happy as you can possibly be; let you forget all your troubles for tonight."
    ks "Puedo hacerte tan feliz como te sea posible; hacerte olvidar todos tus problemas por esta noche."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2947
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_660b7a07:

    # ks "But if you want me to do that for you, Akiko, I need you to give me a nice big smile."
    ks "Pero si quieres que haga eso por ti, Akiko, necesito que me des una gran sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2948
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_bb8e4b4e_1:

    # a "..."
    a "..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2951
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_9acafc45:

    # "Man, it's good to see her at least trying to be happy again."
    "Cielos, es bueno verla al menos intentar ser feliz otra vez."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2952
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_71955456:

    # a "Okay..."
    a "Bien..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2953
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4cbfc75e:

    # ks smile "That's it, Akiko. You're doing really well to smile like that."
    ks smile "Eso es, Akiko. Haces bien en sonreír así."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2954
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_654d424e:

    # "Let's keep this going."
    "Sigamos adelante."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2955
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_5ab75723:

    # ks "Just by smiling right now must be giving you a happy feeling in your heart."
    ks "El solo sonreír ahora mismo debe estarle trayendo un gran sentimiento de felicidad a tu corazón."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2957
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_46e00903:

    # ks "And the more you smile, the more that feeling of happiness grows inside of you. Just building up more and more."
    ks "Y entre más sonríes, más crece ese sentimiento de felicidad. Se vuelve más y más grande."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2958
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_8f9e7b8e:

    # ks "In fact, if you keep smiling like that your heart might become so full of happiness that it's no longer enough just to smile."
    ks "De hecho, si continúas sonriendo así, puede que tu corazón se llene tanto de felicidad que ya no sea suficiente sonreír."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2960
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_c045d402:

    # ks "So if you need to laugh, you'll find yourself doing so effortlessly while remaining as deeply hypnotized as you are."
    ks "Si necesitas reír, te será muy fácil hacerlo y permanecer profundamente hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2963
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b23ca40d:

    # a "Snk... eheh..."
    a "Snc... eje..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2964
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4f3ab974:

    # ks "So effortlessly. So naturally..."
    ks "Tan fácil. Tan natural..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2965
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_49fb0c12:

    # a "Hee...t-teeheehee~"
    a "Ji... t-tijiji."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2966
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f7588215:

    # ks "So carefree..."
    ks "Tan relajante..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2969
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_796b39d4:

    # a "Ahahahahahaha!"
    a "¡Ajajajajajaja!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2970
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_0e230270:

    # ks "So completely, blissfully happy."
    ks "Completa y dichosamente feliz."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2971
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ed8e46bb:

    # a "Hahaha! Aahahahahahahaha!"
    a "¡Jajaja! ¡Aajajajajajajaja!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2972
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_cef10efc:

    # ks "That's right, Akiko. Your heart's so full of joy as you laugh your cares away."
    ks "Eso es, Akiko. Tu corazón está tan lleno de felicidad, al dejar que la risa se lleve tus preocupaciones."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2973
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_7e72b18f:

    # a "HAHAHAHAHAHA!" with vpunch
    a "¡JAJAJAJAJAJA!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2974
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_1b0f7d48:

    # "As Akiko's laughter becomes more forceful I find myself smiling wider and wider."
    "Mientras la risa de Akiko se vuelve más fuerte, mi sonrisa crece más y más."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2975
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_42a48f55:

    # "I truly wanted to bring her a little joy after all the pain I've caused her, but I might be enjoying this almost as much as she is."
    "Te verdad quería traerle algo de alegría después de todo el dolor que le causé, pero tal vez yo lo esté disfrutando tanto como ella."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2976
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_8fd35400:

    # a "HAHAHAHA! Aaah! Hah- HAHAHAHAHA!"
    a "¡JAJAJAJA! ¡Aaah! Aah- ¡JAJAJAJAJA!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2977
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_94e74612:

    # "Unfortunately, her pure laughter that I'm delighted to witness starts to get undercut as she begins to struggle for breath."
    "Desafortunadamente, su risa pura, la cual tengo el deleite de presenciar, comienza a deteriorarse, pues empieza a dificultársele respirar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2978
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_85ad7786:

    # "I think it's time I wound things down."
    "Creo que es momento de bajar el ritmo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2979
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d282054b:

    # ks "Now, I'm going to count down to one and snap my fingers, and when I do so you'll find this happy feeling will stop growing."
    ks "Ahora contaré del tres al uno y chasquearé mis dedos, y cuando lo haga, notarás que esta alegre sensación parará de crecer."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2980
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_5e6e071f:

    # a "Aaahahahahahaha!"
    a "¡Aaajajajajajaja!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2981
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_7b30ab29:

    # ks "You won't need to laugh anymore, but that happiness will stay with you for as long as you want it to, Akiko. Understand?"
    ks "Ya no tendrás que reír, pero esa felicidad se quedará contigo por tanto tiempo como desees, Akiko. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2982
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_322064b4:

    # a "Ahaha y-yessshahahahaaha!"
    a "¡Ajaja s-sssíjajajajaaja!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2983
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_94406170:

    # ks "Wonderful. Three, two and..."
    ks "Maravilloso. Tres, dos y..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2984
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a51ab041:

    # a "Haaah... hahahahaha!"
    a "¡Jaaah... jajajajaja!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2989
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_611fa298:

    # ks "One."
    ks "Uno."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2990
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e1a5b55c:

    # a "Mmmmn... mhmhmhm..."
    a "Mmmn... mjmjmjm..."

