translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_52922633:

    # a uniform_down sigh "Risa, please. Don't do this again." with dissolve
    a uniform_down sigh "Risa, por favor. No hagas esto de nuevo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2633
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_fbb42826:

    # a uniform "Hypnosis? You're all saying Kyou used HYPNOSIS to seduce that girl from his old class and that's why she's upset? Get a GRIP, all of you!" with dissolve
    a uniform "¿Hipnosis? ¿Dicen que Kyou usó HIPNOSIS para seducir a esa chica de su vieja clase, y por eso está molesta? ¡No sean ABSURDOS!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2643
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a38123bb:

    # a uniform sigh "I don't know better, Risa. I'm just not going to villify some boy I barely know because you said so." with dissolve
    a uniform sigh "No soy más lista, Risa. Simplemente no voy a vilipendiar a un chico que apenas conozco solo porque tú lo dices." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2698
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_25f98292:

    # "For a moment, no one breathes. As if the tension was suffocating all of us..."
    "Por un momento, nadie respira. Como si la tensión nos estuviera sofocando a todos..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2700
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_164d4237:

    # t "MISS TACHIBANA!"
    t "¡SEÑORITA TACHIBANA!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2702
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b9b04612:

    # "Risa doesn't look Ms. Chiba's way. Just shares a regretful look with Akiko as the colour drains from her face..."
    "Risa no voltea a ver a la profesora Chiba. Solo comparte una mirada de arrepentimiento con Akiko mientras el color se drena de su rostro."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2710
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_98573222:

    # a "I-it was in the heat of the moment, Miss. She never meant to."
    a "F-fue en el calor del momento, profesora. No era su intención."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2944
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ae986c51:

    # ks "That's good. Just feeling it all seep out now. Every bit of stress tumbling out of your head. Every drop carried away by the spiral." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien. Siente cómo todo sale ahora. Cada gota de estrés escapando de tu cabeza. Cada gota siendo arrastrada por la espiral." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3000
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ebefc5c1:

    # "Akiko's laughter fades as she inhales sharply through her nose to catch her breath. But it's clear from her face that she took my words to heart."
    "La risa de Akiko se desvanece al inhalar fuertemente por su nariz para recobrar el aliento. Pero está claro por su rostro que se tomó mis palabras a pecho."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3001
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_04ee3bb2:

    # "That smile... I take a moment to enjoy the purity of her expression before I do anything else."
    "Esa sonrisa... Me tomo un momento para disfrutar la pureza de su expresión antes de hacer nada más."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3002
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4741a4a2:

    # ks "That's right, Akiko, keeping that happiness as long as you want. And now waking up on a count of three, waking up wide awake and completely refreshed in..."
    ks "Eso es, Akiko, mantén esa felicidad por tanto tiempo como desees. Y ahora despierta a la cuenta de tres, despierta completamente fresca en..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3003
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_265327c7:

    # ks "One, two, three."
    ks "Uno, dos, tres."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3007
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_fbd0c712:

    # "I find myself snapping my fingers for effect once again as I count her back up to wakefulness. It just feels right to do that now."
    "Una vez más chasqueo los dedos por efecto al contar para traerla de vuelta. Siento que funciona muy bien."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3010
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_9d832080:

    # a "Um... wow, that was... r-really something~" with dissolve
    a "Em... guau, eso... e-eso fue..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3011
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_99a433ff:

    # ks "How was that? You feel any better?"
    ks "¿Cómo estuvo? ¿Te sientes mejor?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3013
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_622f3ed6:

    # a "Ahaha, so much better! I can't believe how much lighter I'm feeling about..." with dissolve
    a "¡Jajaja, mucho mejor! No puedo creer lo ligera que me siento ahora respecto a..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3014
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e9f382a5:

    # a "W-well, everything! Hahaha!"
    a "¡P-pues todo! ¡Jajaja!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3016
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_1754064c:

    # "She laughs gently, only to stop suddenly as she seems to have some kind of realization." with dissolve
    "Se ríe con suavidad, para después detenerse súbitamente como si se hubiera dado cuenta de algo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4146
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_61707f82:

    # ks confused "Huh? What's the matter?"
    ks confused "¿Eh? ¿Qué pasa?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3020
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4e486328:

    # a "That was hypnotherapy just now!" with dissolve
    a "¡Eso fue hipnoterapia!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3021
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_6d0bc22d:

    # ks surprised "Uh... was it?"
    ks surprised "Eh... ¿en serio?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3023
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_c311d033:

    # "Akiko smiles and nods at me excitedly." with dissolve
    "Akiko sonríe y asiente con emoción." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3024
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3c3acd8a:

    # a "Yup! I mean, when you think about it, you hypnotized me to treat a problem I was having."
    a "¡Sipi! Pues, si lo piensas, me hipnotizaste para tratar un problema que tenía."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3027
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_60c94915:

    # a "A-and I'm supposed to be the therapist around here... ahahaha~" with dissolve
    a "Y-y se supone que yo sea la terapeuta aquí... jajajaja." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3028
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_bebf3c38:

    # "She giggles playfully, but the moment she says that I'm suddenly reminded of something from this morning..."
    "Se ríe lúdicamente, pero cuando dice eso, recuerdo repentinamente algo de esta mañana."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3038
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_08b67784:

    # r "Your little psych patient is why Hiroko crashed and burned yesterday. But you knew that, didn't you."
    r "Tu disque-paciente psiquiátrico este es la razón por la que Hiroko salió hecha un desastre ayer. Pero tú ya lo sabías, ¿no?"
# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3040
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d680e5a9:

    # "She told me she wanted to be a therapist, but... does she actually think of herself as MY therapist now or what?"
    "Me contó que quería ser terapeuta, pero... ¿ahora cree que es MI terapeuta o qué?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3041
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_8acab1a8:

    # "Because damn, I don't want to be just some personal project to her. Not by a long shot."
    "Porque, diablos, no quiero ser solo un proyecto personal para ella. Nada de eso."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3042
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ed31dc24:

    # ks smirk "I don't know, Akiko. You seem like a high school student to me."
    ks smirk "No lo sé, Akiko. Para mí luces como una estudiante de preparatoria."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3044
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_dcc50f2d:

    # a "Hehe... that's fair~" with dissolve
    a "Jeje... es cierto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3045
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_fd954cfa:

    # "I want to be so much more to her than that."
    "Quiero ser mucho más para ella que eso."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3046
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_1fcc1f12:

    # ks smile "Call it hypnotherapy if you want, but I just wanted to help put the smile back on your face."
    ks smile "Llámalo hipnoterapia si quieres, pero yo simplemente quería ayudar a volver a poner una sonrisa en tu rostro."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3047
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_899a776d:

    # ks "Just like how you've helped put it back on mine, Akiko."
    ks "Como tú ayudaste a volver a ponerla en el mío, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3056
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_8f533376:

    # a "Aww!" with dissolve
    a "¡Ooh!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3058
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_582b0c97:

    # "As Akiko hums cheerfully to herself, it becomes harder to recall how despondent she seemed just a few minutes ago."
    "Al oír a Akiko tararear alegremente para sí misma, es difícil recordar lo abatida que se veía hace solo unos pocos minutos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3059
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_2931c153:

    # a "W-well, right now I feel like we could beat anything that comes our way."
    a "B-bueno, ahora mismo siento que podemos con cualquier cosa que encontremos en nuestro camino."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4180
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_a9a83234:

    # a "So thank you, Kyou. We'll get through this mess together, okay?" with dissolve
    a "Así que, gracias, Kyou. Superaremos este desastre juntos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3062
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_0fd8ff45:

    # "The atmosphere has just completely turned on its head."
    "La atmósfera dio una vuelta completa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3063
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_103efb35:

    # ks "Okay!"
    ks "¡De acuerdo!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3069
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_2014d472:

    # a "Mmm... hypnosis really is amazing if it can make you feel like this~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a "Mmm... La hipnosis sí que es asombrosa si puede hacerte sentir así~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3070
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ef67211f:

    # ks happy blush "Y-yeah!"
    ks happy blush "¡S-sí!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3071
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_0b04cb3a:

    # "Man, she's giving off so much positivity right now I think it might be rubbing off on me."
    "Caray, está irradiando tanta positividad que creo que me está contagiando."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3072
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4a80de24:

    # ks smile "And... i-if you think that was amazing you haven't seen anything yet!"
    ks smile "¡Y... s-si crees que eso es asombroso, aún no has visto nada!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3074
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d383f6a4:

    # a "Oh, yeah?" with dissolve
    a "Oh, ¿de veras?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3075
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_2fcecdb1:

    # ks "Yeah! Maybe you want me to show you?"
    ks "¡Sí! ¿Tal vez quieras que te muestre?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3076
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e8e04757:

    # a "I, um..."
    a "Pues, em..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3077
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_1c57bdf7:

    # "Her breath catches for a moment as she hesitates..."
    "Aguanta el aliento, dudando por un instante..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3079
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_15392d57:

    # a "Show me what?" with dissolve
    a "¿Mostrarme qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3080
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_9e0f9e16:

    # ks "Well, I was just thinking... u-umm..."
    ks "Pues, estaba pensando... e-emm..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3081
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_13a335b3:

    # "But it feels like we've both come too far to stop now."
    "Pero parece que ya hemos llegado muy lejos para detenernos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3082
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_552a70d5:

    # a "No, it's okay. Just tell me what you're thinking, whatever it is. I want you to tell me."
    a "No, descuida. Solo dime lo que estás pensando, sea lo que sea. Quiero que me lo digas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4198
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_7d8a4de1:

    # ks "O-okay, this is gonna sound a little crazy so bear with me."
    ks "M-muy bien, esto sonará un tanto loco, pero solo escucha."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3084
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4d0814ff:

    # ks "But I was thinking we could try binding your feelings to an object. Like, just some everyday object..."
    ks "Pensaba que podríamos intentar vincular tus sentimientos a un objeto. Un objeto cualquiera..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3087
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_5b0c5cf2:

    # "I hold up my phone again as I try to explain the thoughts excitedly forming in my head." with dissolve
    "Sostengo otra vez mi teléfono, intentando explicar las ideas que se forman con emoción en mi cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3088
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_687a85a3:

    # ks "Like my phone. And you could feel everything that happens to it as if it happened to yourself. Like it was some kind of voodoo doll or... w-whatever."
    ks "Como mi teléfono. Y podrías sentir todo lo que le pase como si te estuviera pasando a ti. Como alguna clase de muñeco vudú o..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3090
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_b01efbe8:

    # a "W-wow... and you can do that with hypnosis?" with dissolve
    a "G-guau... ¿y se puede hacer eso con hipnosis?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3091
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_55f26a33:

    # ks "Yeah! I-I mean, I dunno if WE can do that, but I just... yeah, I just thought it'd be a neat trick if we could pull that off."
    ks "¡Sí! B-bueno, no sé si NOSOTROS podamos, pero, pues... sí, solo pensé que sería un buen truco si lo podemos lograr."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3093
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_dc44ea1e:

    # ks "But what do you think? We could have some fun trying to make it work?" with dissolve
    ks "Pero ¿tú qué opinas? ¿Podríamos divertirnos intentando hacerlo funcionar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3094
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f7a5cfca:

    # ks "I-If you want to, I mean..."
    ks "S-si tú quieres, claro..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3096
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4bb4eac9:

    # a "Let's try it!" with dissolve
    a "¡Intentémoslo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3097
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_edca7c88:

    # "I'm getting a really giddy feeling in my gut as Akiko happily agrees without missing a beat."
    "Siento vértigo en mi estómago al escuchar a Akiko aceptar felizmente sin vacilar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3098
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d571c66f:

    # "I'm so goddamn pumped that Akiko's gotten into hypnosis as much as I have!"
    "¡Estoy tan emocionado de que a Akiko le esté gustando la hipnosis tanto como a mí!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3099
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_8c6f88fa:

    # ks "O-okay, so I'm going to ask you to stare at the spiral again, alright? I need you to focus."
    ks "M-muy bien, pues voy a pedirte que mires la espiral otra vez, ¿de acuerdo? Quiero que te concentres."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3101
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_5f4d77c6:

    # "The spiral app lights back up as I switch my phone back on, and Akiko's attention quickly returns to the pattern as it looms large in front of her eager eyes." with dissolve
    "La aplicación de espiral vuelve a brillar en cuanto enciendo mi teléfono, y la atención de Akiko pronto regresa al gran patrón que se encuentra frente a sus entusiasmados ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3103
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_7d70fcae:

    # ks smile noblush "Take a deep breath and relax now. Focus your eyes on the spiral and let yourself be drawn into its hypnotic swirl..."
    ks smile noblush "Ahora respira profundamente y relájate. Enfoca tus ojos en la espiral y déjate llevar por su hipnótico movimiento..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3106
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_3ca21f85:

    # a "Okay... wow..." with dissolve
    a "Muy bien... guau..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3107
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_02bf7a2d:

    # ks "Becoming completely focused. Becoming completely drawn in by the hypnotic swirls, so easily. So familiarly..."
    ks "Completamente enfocada. Completamente atraída por este patrón hipnótico, muy fácilmente. Te resulta tan familiar..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3108
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_bc817b9a:

    # ks "So effortlessly until soon you can see only the spiral. Hear only the sound of my voice."
    ks "Tan relajante. Hasta que pronto solo puedes ver la espiral. Solo puedes escuchar mi voz."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3109
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_94791dab:

    # ks "Allowing everything else to slip away as you fall deeper and deeper into hypnosis."
    ks "Dejando que todo lo demás se desvanezca al caer más y más profundo en hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3113
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_ed8d172a:

    # ks "Deeper and deeper... that's right, Akiko."
    ks "Más y más profundo... eso es, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3114
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_550e31a5:

    # "I can see Akiko's eyes glaze over and her eyelids flicker as she drops straight back into her hypnotized state."
    "Puedo ver los ojos de Akiko ponerse vidriosos y sus párpados temblar al caer de vuelta en estado de hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3115
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_c1f43ba0:

    # "Compared with how difficult it was to hypnotize her the first time, it's incredibly rewarding to see her drop so easily now just by showing her the spiral app."
    "Comparado con lo difícil que fue hipnotizarla la primera vez, es increíblemente gratificante verla caer tan fácilmente ahora solo al mostrarle la espiral."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3116
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_579b0862:

    # ks "Deeper and deeper, letting your subconscious mind open up and accept the reality we both want to create."
    ks "Más y más profundo, dejando que tu subconsciente se abra y acepte la realidad que ambos queremos crear."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3117
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_428dc6b9:

    # ks "And in this new reality... your physical feelings are bound to this phone that I'm holding in front of you."
    ks "Y esta es tu nueva realidad... tus sensaciones físicas están vinculadas a este teléfono que sostengo ante ti."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3118
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4ddf2afa:

    # ks "Focus entirely on the phone, Akiko."
    ks "Concéntrate completamente en el teléfono, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3120
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f179d5e6:

    # ks "So for example if I were to touch the very top of this phone, you would feel the same touch on the top of your head..."
    ks "Así que, por ejemplo, si toco la parte de arriba de este teléfono, sentirás el mismo toque en tu cabeza..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3122
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_e10e216c:

    # ks "And if I touch anywhere else, you will feel it exactly where you would expect to feel it. Understand?"
    ks "Y si toco cualquier otra parte, lo sentirás exactamente donde lo esperarías. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3124
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_48e7f29d:

    # a "I understand..." with dissolve
    a "Comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3126
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_f89d168d:

    # "... Is this really going to work? It feels nuts explaining it to her like this." with dissolve
    "... ¿De verdad funcionará? Parece muy alocado al explicárselo así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3127
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4b9ec0cd:

    # "But she's taken to hypnosis so enthusiastically now, taking it all in her stride."
    "Pero ya ha aceptado la hipnosis con mucho entusiasmo y la ha tomado muy bien."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3128
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_c886eeca:

    # "She's fascinated. She wants this to work just as much as I do."
    "Está fascinada. Quiere que esto funcione tanto como yo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3129
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_37cf6e6d:

    # ks "That's wonderful, Akiko. Your subconscious taking all of this in, making it very much a part of your reality."
    ks "Maravilloso, Akiko. Tu subconsciente lo absorbe todo, volviéndolo parte de tu realidad."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3131
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_7772cc0e:

    # "And with that I switch my phone back off and set it aside for now as I eagerly prepare to bring her out of trance once again." with dissolve
    "Y dicho eso, vuelvo a apagar mi teléfono y lo hago a un lado por ahora, preparándome con ansias para despertarla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3132
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_025010ec:

    # ks "And now waking up on a count of three, Akiko. Waking up wide awake and refreshed on one..."
    ks "Y ahora despierta a la cuenta de tres, Akiko. Sintiéndote fresca en uno..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3133
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_392db948:

    # ks "Two..."
    ks "Dos..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3137
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_d8e6d5fa:

    # ks "Three." with dissolve
    ks "Tres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3138
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_277561f9:

    # "Akiko breathes deeply as her eyes quickly blink back into life. Like my snapping fingers flipped a switch in her brain."
    "Akiko respira profundo y sus ojos vuelven rápidamente a la vida. Como si el chasquido de mis dedos hubiera movido un interruptor en su cerebro."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3141
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_6338ae95:

    # a "Is it... d-did you do it already?" with dissolve
    a "¿Está... y-ya lo hiciste?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3143
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_9da6538c:

    # "As a hypnotist this is all just so satisfying to witness."
    "Como hipnotista, es muy satisfactorio presenciar esto."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3144
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_452ff4ec:

    # ks "I think so. Do you want to believe I did?"
    ks "Creo que sí. ¿Quieres creer que lo hice?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3145
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_44e6b779:

    # a "I..."
    a "Eh..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3147
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_4e1c9d6e:

    # a "Y-yeah, I do~" with dissolve
    a "S-sí, sí quiero." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:3151
translate spanish Day8_Redemption_Spiral_913baace:

    # "Smiling, I reach back to my phone and carefully pick it up in front of her, just holding it at the sides..."
