# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1598
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_29a99b56:

    # n side sad_side "I see... go on." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Ya veo... continúa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1600
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_fa6fdcfb:

    # ks "It didn't matter what I thought about it. You wanted me to put on a show for you and your buddies, and that's all that mattered."
    ks "No importó lo que yo opinara. Tú querías que diera un espectáculo para ti y tus amigas, y eso es todo lo que importaba."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1601
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1870841e:

    # ks "But more than that... do you even respect me at all, Nozomi?"
    ks "Pero más que eso... ¿siquiera me respetas, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1602
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d34f2936:

    # n surprised "Huh?" with dissolve
    n surprised "¿Eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1603
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f7e9cc01:

    # ks "I mean, everyone thinks I'm some weird creep. I know what you all say about me behind my back."
    ks "Quiero decir, todos creen que soy un bicho raro. Sé lo que dicen a mis espaldas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1605
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_caa585aa:

    # ks "But you've been bringing me into your life and I thought at least you were coming around on me. I thought you were starting to like me." with dissolve
    ks "Pero me dejaste entrar en tu vida y pensé que empezarías a verme diferente. Pensé que comenzaba a agradarte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1606
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_893958cb:

    # ks "But you don't. Not really."
    ks "Pero supongo que no."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1609
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a5c1eb45:

    # ks "So that's what I think, Nozomi. I'm just someone for you to control."
    ks "Eso es lo que pienso, Nozomi. No soy más que alguien a quien puedes controlar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1610
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_cddd2820:

    # "... Man, I really did unload everything on her."
    "... Caray, en serio lo saqué todo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1611
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1810ac1a:

    # "Maybe I went too far, but... but, it's what she wanted, right?"
    "Tal vez fui muy lejos, pero... pero es lo que ella quería, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1612
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_693e1f0f:

    # n sleeptalk "... Thank you, Kyou. For being up-front with me." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "... Gracias, Kyou. Por ser directo conmigo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1613
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_00af7257:

    # ks "Yeah..."
    ks "Sí..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1614
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d00f4400:

    # n neutral_left "I really am horrible, aren't I." with dissolve
    n neutral_left "En verdad soy horrible, ¿no es así? " with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1615
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c4aff0a1:

    # "I let out a shuddered sigh, and watch as Nozomi chews her lip while her eyes waver, like she could burst into tears at any moment."
    "Dejo salir un fatigado suspiro, y observo a Nozomi morderse el labio mientras sus ojos tiemblan, como si fueran a romper en llanto en cualquier momento."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1616
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_8719e631:

    # "But just then, I spy her reaching into her school bag as a frown starts to form on her pretty features."
    "Pero entonces, la veo tomar su mochila, con su seño frunciéndose entre sus bellos rasgos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1618
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_4206d2ee:

    # n irritated "So you wouldn't want a person like me..." with dissolve
    n irritated "Entonces no querrías que una persona como yo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1620
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b091cfc1:

    # n "... to hypnotize you again, would you?"
    n "... te hipnotizara de nuevo, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1620
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7c1b2fca:

    # "My eyes widen as Nozomi suddenly stands upright and I see in her hand..."
    "Veo atónito cómo Nozomi se levanta y noto en su mano..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1622
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a41aab11:

    # n "Hypnosis can only work when there's a bond of trust between the hypnotist and their subject."
    n "La hipnosis solo puede funcionar cuando hay un vínculo de confianza entre el hipnotista y su sujeto."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1625
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_4dab6e50:

    # n "Am I wrong?"
    n "¿O me equivoco?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1627
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5c5f27e9:

    # k "N... Nozomi?!"
    k "¡¿N... Nozomi?!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1627
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_49cea505:

    # "What... what's happening? What is she saying?"
    "¿Qué... qué está pasando? ¿Qué está diciendo?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1628
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6079974d:

    # n "But in spite of what you just said... you still want me to hypnotize you."
    n "Pero a pesar de lo que dijiste... aún quieres que te hipnotice."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1629
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_4c123d70:

    # "She holds that penlight aloft and suddenly my mind is doing flips."
    "Sostiene la linterna en lo alto y de pronto mi mente comienza a dar vueltas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1630
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_3d90c786:

    # n "Don't you."
    n "¿No es cierto?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1646
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_40ed5deb:

    # k "I... u-uhhh..."
    k "Yo... e-eeeh..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1646
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_54b8d18d:

    # n "I need you to answer me, Kyou. And you will."
    n "Debes responderme, Kyou. Y lo harás."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1648
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_8adf3990:

    # n "So. Do you want me to hypnotize you again? Right here and now?"
    n "¿Y bien? ¿Quieres que te hipnotice otra vez? ¿Aquí y ahora?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1649
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_66ac253b:

    # "I can only watch as time seems to stand still."
    "Solo puedo mirar y el tiempo parece detenerse."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1658
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7fb398a1:

    # "I can't... I just can't say no to this woman. Not any more."
    "No puedo... No puedo decirle que no a esta mujer. Ya no puedo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1661
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0b78d6f8:

    # n "Being hypnotized by me just feels too good to turn down now, doesn't it?" with dissolve
    n "Ser hipnotizado por mí se siente muy bien para rechazarlo, ¿no es así?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1635
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_daac0f55:

    # n "Y-you think I don't care about you? Like you're just a toy for me to play with? Well, so what?"
    n "¿C-crees que no me importas? ¿Que eres solo un juguete para mi diversión? Bueno, ¿y qué?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1669
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_95b0a920:

    # n "Why does any of that matter when the only thing you want in all the world is to listen to my voice and feel the thrill of going deeper and deeper for me." with dissolve
    n "¿Qué importa eso si lo único que quieres en el mundo es escuchar mi voz y sentir la emoción de caer más y más profundo para mí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1670
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9f5be02d:

    # n "Because that IS what you want to happen, isn't it?"
    n "Porque eso ES lo que quieres que ocurra, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1671
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_759cfb11:

    # k "I... I-I..."
    k "Y-... y-yo..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1669
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_72a4a7fc:

    # n "Answer."
    n "Responde."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1680
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ae18db05:

    # n "You're going to go so, so deep for me, and by the time I let you wake you'll be completely under my control." with dissolve
    n "Vas a caer muy, muy profundo para mí, y para cuando te permita despertar, estarás completamente bajo mi control." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1677
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9f0402dd:

    # n blush "I'll make you sing. I'll make you dance, I'll... m-make you into my hypnotic toy boy who'll do anything I desire." with dissolve
    n blush "Te haré cantar. Te haré bailar. Te... ha-haré mi juguete hipnótico que hará todo lo que desee." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1679
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_80ad963a:

    # n "By the time I'm done with you, you'll be my obedient dog who wants nothing more than to wag his little tail and follow me always, doing every little thing I say."
    n "Para cuando termine contigo, serás mi obediente cachorro que no quiere más que mover la colita y seguirme siempre, haciendo cada cosa que le diga."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1680
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_8af71f75:

    # n smirk "I'll destroy you and... y-you'll love it. I'll MAKE you love it. You know I can." with dissolve
    n smirk "Te destruiré y... t-te va a encantar. HARÉ que te encante. Sabes que puedo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1681
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f8b4cb85:

    # n "And even knowing all of that, you still want this, Kyou. You still want to go deep for me, even knowing everything I said is true."
    n "E incluso sabiendo todo eso, aún quieres eso, Kyou. Aún quieres ir muy profundo para mí, incluso sabiendo que todo lo que dije es verdad."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1685
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7dd75cd4:

    # n angry "Say it!" with dissolve
    n angry "¡Dilo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1702
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7c201f6b:

    # n "That's right. You won't resist me, Kyou. You can't resist me. It feels too good to resist because... b-because..."
    n "Así es. No vas a resistirte a mí, Kyou. No puedes resistirte a mí. Se siente demasiado bien como para resistirse porque... p-porque..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1714
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d671a0cb:

    # n neutral noblush "... It feels so good to be hypnotized by Nozomi." with dissolve
    n neutral noblush "... Se siente muy bien ser hipnotizado por Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1699
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c43c2302:

    # n cry "Oh... o-oh my god, Kyou..." with dissolve
    n cry "Oh... o-oh, por Dios, Kyou..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1721
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a3c7966e:

    # n frightened "W-what have I done to you?"
    n frightened "¿Qu-qué te he hecho?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1702
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_394e219a:

    # n "{cps=15}What have I {/cps}{nw}"
    n "{cps=15}¡¿Qué he {/cps}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1703
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_bcaeaa02:

    # extend "DONE?!" with vpunch
    extend "HECHO?!" with vpunch

