# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1244
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_372eb661:

    # "And imagining those beautiful brown eyes again. That siren song of a voice when she talks..."
    "Y volver a imaginar esos hermosos ojos cafés. Ese canto de sirena en su voz..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1265
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_07c569b7:

    # h "Urrrgh, seriously, Nozo?" with dissolve
    h "Ayyy, ¿en serio, Nozo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1505
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_bc54f8de:

    # "She may not want the truth of what we're doing to get out, but how is driving those girls away any better for her?"
    "Puede que no quiera que la verdad sobre lo que hemos estado haciendo salga a la luz, ¿pero alejar a esas chicas le parece mejor?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1506
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_10b3d03a:

    # "But more to the point... where does that leave us?"
    "Pero más importante... ¿eso dónde nos deja?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1626
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1fab365b:

    # "... her penlight. She's showing it to me here? In school of all places?"
    "... su linterna. ¿Me la está mostrando? ¿Y además en la escuela?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1652
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_01a35899:

    # n "It's a simple question. You don't need to think about it."
    n "Es una pregunta simple. No necesitas pensarlo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1653
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ac7906aa:

    # n "So just tell me."
    n "Simplemente dime."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1680
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_77860322:

    # n "So you understand what's about to happen, Kyou. I'm going to show you the light again and I'm going to lull you all the way back into a deep, hypnotic trance."
    n " Entonces entiendes lo que está por suceder, Kyou. Voy a mostrarte la luz otra vez y te arrullaré hasta un profundo trance hipnótico."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1752
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7458be33:

    # k "Nozomi..."
    k "Nozomi..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1846
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_fead5211:

    # ks "It's gotta be the only reason we could go as deep into hypnosis as we did, and it's the only reason I took so well to all of those crazy things you put in my head."
    ks "Debe ser la única razón por la que caímos tan profundo en hipnosis, y única razón por la que absorbí tan bien todas las locuras que pusiste en mi cabeza."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2022-09-09 08:19

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1393
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_16e7f45a:

    # s uniform_handup smile "I would agree. There does seem to be something you are not telling us." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup smile "Concuerdo. Da la impresión de haber algo que no nos estás diciendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1496
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e3211983:

    # s concerned_right "Well, I believe you and him need to talk things through." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Bueno, me parece que él y tú necesitan hablar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1512
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a6084ec6:

    # "I really don't want her to drive me away, like she's driven everyone else from this rooftop that's seeming lonelier by the minute."
    "De verdad no quiero que me aleje, como ha alejado a todos de esta azotea que parece más solitaria cada minuto."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1609
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d37c8e2a:

    # ks "You don't want to date me. You don't want me as your friend..." with dissolve
    ks "No quieres salir conmigo. No me quieres como amigo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1610
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_eb1cb0f1:

    # ks "All I am to you is some guy you can hypnotize to get your rocks off. I'm just some kind of toy to you."
    ks "Todo lo que soy para ti es un chico al que puedes hipnotizar por tu propio placer. No soy más que una especie de juguete."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1626
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5f30ab2c:

    # n "So if the subject really despises their hypnotist so much, there's no way in hell they would open their mind to them ever again."
    n " Por lo que, si el sujeto realmente desprecia tanto a su hipnotista, bajo ningún concepto volverá a abrirle las puertas de su mente."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1757
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9b7b7122:

    # n "But I'm going to do better for you, I swear."
    n "Pero voy a hacer las cosas bien por ti ahora, lo juro."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:1878
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_cdf6d71d:

    # "And I can't help but smile. As it is, I can already feel the tension I was holding start to seep out of me."
    "Y no puedo evitar sonreír. Ya hasta empiezo a sentir la tensión que tenía guardada comenzar a drenarse."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2050
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_cf0da467:

    # "I see that gentle smile on her lips, and feel her calm hand resting over mine, and I can't help but smile back."
    "Puedo ver una dulce sonrisa en sus labios, y sentir su mano posada tranquilamente sobre la mía, y no puedo evitar devolver la sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2181
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7ea2d8b2:

    # ks "... You really could hypnotize me again sometime?"
    ks "... ¿De verdad podrías volver a hipnotizarme alguna vez?"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2022-09-30 13:47

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2811
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f95d91f9:

    # "I take all this excitement with me into the next day."
    "Traigo conmigo la misma emoción al día siguiente."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2814
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_28c37783:

    # "Not to mention how much I'm going to impress everyone in that online hypnosis community."
    "Sin mencionar cuánto impresionaré a todos en esa comunidad de hipnosis en línea."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2815
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e9e673b2:

    # "I could become a legend in there. Maybe even beyond there..."
    "Podría convertirme en una leyenda para ellos. Tal vez incluso más..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2819
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6f608ef9:

    # "Like... wow, I never could've imagined when I started to learn hypnosis that it'd lead to this. Never in a million years."
    "O sea... guau, nunca me habría imaginado cuando comencé a aprender hipnosis que me llevaría a esto. Ni en un millón de años."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2820
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6cf5dbeb:

    # "But I don't regret a thing I've done this past year. Not any more."
    "Pero no me arrepiento de nada de lo que hice este año. Ya no más."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2821
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d1b222bd:

    # "For the first time in years... life feels good to me."
    "Por primera vez en años... la vida se siente bien."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2825
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_82c0318a:

    # "I leisurely walk into class and prepare to take my seat to start the school week."
    "Camino plácidamente a clase y me preparo para tomar asiento y dar comienzo a la semana de escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2832
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e1827608:

    # "But before I reach my desk, I notice Hiroko and her friends just ahead..."
    "Pero antes de llegar a mi escritorio, noto a Hiroko y sus amigas adelante..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2833
translate spanish Day8_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f96c9930:

    # h "S-so yeah, I'm super sorry about yesterday, Nozo. Just bailing on everybody like that."
    h "Y-y este, sí, lo siento mucho por lo de ayer, Nozo. Haber huido de todas así."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2834
