    ks "Eso es. Tu cuerpo se queda tieso, tus pensamientos se desvanecen, tus ojos se cierran..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2613
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_1319bbe5:

    # ks "{cps=20}Letting those tired eyes close and... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks "{cps=20}Deja que esos cansados ojos se cierren y... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2616
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_7bd439e8:

    # extend "sleep, Hiroko. That's right."
    extend "duerme, Hiroko. Eso es."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2617
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_95dcdac4:

    # "Just as I expected, bringing her back into this state was child's play, no matter how hard she tried to fight it."
    "Tal como esperaba, regresarla a este estado fue un juego de niños, sin importar cuánto intentara resistirse."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2618
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_2a788460:

    # ks "Nice and deep asleep now. Going so much deeper, as your body remains absolutely still. Your body completely fixed in place."
    ks "Profundamente dormida. Cayendo muy profundo, a la vez que tu cuerpo permanece absolutamente inmóvil. Completamente fijo en su posición."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2619
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_e869ed5c:

    # "My penlight is a dangerous and powerful tool, no doubt about that."
    "Mi linterna es una peligrosa y poderosa herramienta, de eso no hay duda."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2620
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_6e401ae9:

    # "But don't worry, Hiroko. I'm not... I'm not going to abuse it like you think I will."
    "No te preocupes, Hiroko. No voy a... no voy a abusar de ella como crees que lo haré."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2621
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_f6ab4b0c:

    # ks "And all the while feeling so safe, so relaxed, so ready to listen to my voice as my words take you even deeper. Even deeper."
    ks "Te sientes completamente segura, y relajada, y lista para escuchar mi voz, dejando que mis palabras te lleven más profundo. Más y más profundo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2622
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_27b271e8:

    # "That's my promise to you."
    "Te hago esa promesa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2623
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_5ed40a60:

    # ks "Now very soon you'll find you won't remember a thing about what we've been doing, or why you were so afraid of me. And that's okay."
    ks "Muy bien, pronto no recordarás nada de lo que hemos estado haciendo, ni por qué me tenías miedo. Y eso está bien."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2624
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_7a21a4dc:

    # "So you can just leave me alone."
    "Así que puedes simplemente dejarme solo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2625
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_62ea68db:

    # ks "Because I'll give you some new memories about what happened. You'll accept these memories, and let them become your truth."
    ks "Porque te daré nuevos recuerdos sobre lo que pasó. Aceptarás esos recuerdos, y los volverás tu verdad."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2626
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_5e2b5f27:

    # ks "Understand, Hiroko?"
    ks "¿Comprendes, Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2628
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_1a2f318f:

    # h "Yeah... I understand..." with dissolve
    h "Sí... comprendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:2630
translate spanish Day8_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_27592880:

    # ks "Good. So listen very carefully..." with dissolve
