    a "C-compañeras..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4852
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_9ba4bbbd:

    # "It seems Nozomi's sudden appearance has put them all on edge; their irrelevant arguments dying on their lips as she comes to a stop before us."
    "Parece que la repentina aparición de Nozomi las pone tensas a todas; sus irrelevantes argumentos se desvanecen de sus labios al verla pararse ante nosotros."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4853
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_4b6d05a3:

    # n sad_closed "Oh, Akiko. Could you really not help yourself? After everything we talked about?" with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Oh, Akiko. ¿De verdad no pudiste resistirte? ¿Después de todo lo que hablamos?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4854
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_c73b93f1:

    # "And I look at her, unchanged from the moment we parted; with those new glasses sitting perfectly on her nose that mimic the girl she's replaced in my heart."
    "Y yo la veo, sin cambio alguno desde el momento en que nos apartamos; con esos bellos anteojos sobre su nariz que imitan a la chica que reemplazó en mi corazón."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4855
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_85e8a9cc:

    # a confused_side "I-I know, but it just felt so, um... right? To keep looking like this?" with dissolve
    a confused_side "L-lo sé, pero me hace sentir tan, em... ¿cómoda? El seguir viéndome así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4856
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_8c875083:

    # "She's still the same Nozomi from before. Everything I told her holds true, no matter what anybody might have said to her after they wrenched her away from me."
    "Sigue siendo la misma Nozomi que antes. Sigue creyendo en mis palabras, sin importar lo que nadie le haya dicho después de alejarla de mí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4857
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_a7f152d7:

    # a sad_side2 "You understand, right? I just want to keep it a little longer." with dissolve
    a sad_side2 "Lo entiendes, ¿verdad? Solo quiero quedarme así un poco más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4858
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_d0751840:

    # "That intervention at the tennis court didn't do shit. So maybe now I can finally talk to her."
    "Esa intervención en la cancha de tenis no hizo una mierda. Así que tal vez aún pueda hablar con ella."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4863
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_a57bb626:

    # ks smile "Hey. You got a minute? I really need to talk to you." with dissolve
    ks smile "Oye. ¿Tienes un minuto? En serio necesito hablar contigo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4867
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_be63beca:

    # a sad2 "Oh, um... y-you know I'd... love to, but..." with dissolve
    a sad2 "Oh, em... s-sabes que me... encantaría, pero..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4869
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_5b7c1014:

    # a sad_side2 "We all need to get to homeroom, right?" with dissolve
    a sad_side2 "Tenemos que entrar a clase, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4870
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f0232d8a:

    # "It's hard not to notice her wary glance towards the other girls in our company as she talks."
    "Es difícil no notar la cautelosa mirada que les da a las otras chicas que nos acompañan."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4871
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_a4a9bcf5:

    # n frown "That's right, Kyou. We don't want to miss homeroom, do we." with dissolve
    n frown "Así es, Kyou. No queremos perdernos la clase, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4872
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_50a546ec:

    # "And of course, her attention on one girl in particular."
    "Y por supuesto, su atención en una de las chicas en particular."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4873
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_c05bedff:

    # h angry "An' that means our OWN classrooms, so don't start any shit!" with dissolve
    h angry "Y con eso se refiere a la que habrá en NUESTRO salón, ¡así que no salgas con alguna pendejada!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4875
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_94d08f57:

    # ks neutral "We still have ten minutes. Homeroom can wait a little longer; this won't take long." with dissolve
    ks neutral "Aún tenemos diez minutos. La clase puede esperar un poco más; esto no tardará mucho." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4876
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_bb4ddacf:

    # s irritated "Kyou, if you think we are leaving you alone with Akiko for even a moment, you are more deluded than I even thought possible." with dissolve
    s irritated "Kyou, si crees que te dejaremos a solas con Akiko incluso por un momento, eres más iluso de lo que creí posible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4877
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_69391b40:

    # ks frown "What do you think I'm even gonna do to her out here? I just want to talk."
    ks frown "¿Pues qué piensan que le voy a hacer? Solo quiero hablar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4880
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_75555065:

    # a uniform3 sad_closed "Ah, p-please stop fighting. I don't want to cause any more trouble for anybody else." with dissolve
    a uniform3 sad_closed "Ah, p-por favor, dejen de pelear. No quiero causarle más problemas a nadie." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4881
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f139c691:

    # a sad "Let's just go inside and we'll talk about this later. Okay, Kyou?" with dissolve
    a sad "Mejor hay que entrar y hablaremos de esto después. ¿Está bien, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4882
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_36204262:

    # "She glances anxiously back in my direction as she says that. And... yeah, this was never going to work. I need to be more patient."
    "Ella volta ansiosamente en mi dirección al decir eso. Y... sí, está claro que esto no iba a funcionar. Debo ser más paciente."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4883
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_46547ec2:

    # ks "Fffine..."
    ks "Bieeen..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4884
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_e11dfc39:

    # "They can't stop us forever, can they?"
    "No pueden detenernos por siempre, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4885
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b25bee12:

    # n irritated "Let's go, then." with dissolve
    n irritated "Pues andando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4892
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b36f8284:

    # "So they all turn and walk themselves to class and... huh, that's a long bag Nozomi's holding, close to her regular school bag."
    "Entonces todas se dan la vuelta para caminar a clase y... ¿eh? No había notado esa bolsa tan larga que lleva Nozomi junto a la usual."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4893
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_aaa0a7ce:

    # "Why would she have something like that unless... no, it couldn't be. It must be something she's bringing for the student council."
    "¿Por qué llevaría una cosa así? A no ser que... No, no puede ser. Tiene que ser algo para el consejo estudiantil."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4894
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_9d237baf:

    # "Besides, she told me she was gonna quit doing that crap."
    "Además, me dijo que dejaría esa estupidez."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4897
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ebe17d25:

    # "Pushing that bit of weirdness out of my mind, I show up to class a little behind those other girls and settle in for another long morning."
    "Ignorando ese extraño detalle de momento, llego a la clase un poco después de las otras chicas y me preparo para una larga mañana."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4901
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_63aca58b:

    # "But just as I sit down, I feel my phone as it hums in my pocket..."
    "Pero justo cuando llego a mi lugar, siento mi teléfono vibrar en mi bolsillo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4902
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_94fc97fe:

    # "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Sorry.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Lo siento.\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4903
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_053f9364:

    # "I keep my phone under my desk as I cast a furtive glance at my tormentors ahead."
    "Mantengo mi teléfono bajo mi escritorio, lanzándoles una mirada furtiva a mis atormentadoras sentadas delante."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4904
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_0fcf6e38:

    # "But at least for now they seem to be ignoring me and talking amongst themselves."
    "Pero al menos por ahora parecen estar ignorándome y hablando entre ellas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4905
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ef905337:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"I've been trying to get a hold of you all night, you know.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Estuve tratando de comunicarme contigo toda la noche, ¿sabes?\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4907
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_7e37ef08:

    # "{color=#5F5C5C}\"I know Im really sorry. Just been a lot going on.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Lo se lo siento. Es que hubo muchas cosas sucediendo.\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4908
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b97c6f1a:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"Yeah, I'm sorry too. I shouldn't have left you like that.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Sí, yo también lo siento. No debí dejarte así.\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4910
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_9f8c32d8:

    # "Just then, I can sense those girls casting me a glance over their shoulders, and I'm quick to take my eyes off the phone and stare moodily into the distance."
    "En ese momento siento a esas chicas echándome una mirada sobre el hombro, y rápidamente le+ quito los ojos a la pantalla y volteo a la distancia."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4911
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f478cc68:

    # "I'm sure they suspect I'm up to something, so I'd better make this quick."
    "Seguro sospechan que tengo algo entre manos, así que mejor hago esto rápido."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4915
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_1d0525b4:

    # "But as their attentions quickly turn back to each other, and I return mine to the phone in my lap, Nozomi has already messaged me again."
    "Pero cuando su atención regresa rápidamente a su charla, y la mía al teléfono en mi regazo, Nozomi ya me envió otro mensaje."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4916
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_e410a332:

    # "{color=#5F5C5C}\"We're still having lunch together right?\"{/color}"
    "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Aún vamos a almorzar juntos verdad?\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4917
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_468feea7:

    # "And I fight to suppress the smile that creeps upon my lips."
    "Y yo lucho por suprimir la sonrisa que busca formarse en mis labios."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4918
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_9c4cd892:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"I wish. But you know those girls won't leave us alone.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Eso quisiera. Pero ya sabes que esas chicas no nos van a dejar en paz.\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4919
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b99d5b28:

    # "My Nozomi's coming through for me, just as I knew she would. I only need to nudge her in the right direction."
    "Sabía que mi Nozomi aún querría conectar conmigo. Solo necesito empujarla en la dirección correcta."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4921
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_4e9d12bc:

    # "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Right...\"{/color}"
    "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Cierto...\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4922
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_503ddd0d:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"I really need to talk to you though, so let's meet after school. We could go to my house?\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Pero en serio necesito hablar contigo, así que hay que reunirnos después de la escuela. ¿Qué tal en mi casa?\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4926
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b0078d41:

    # t "Okay class, settle down. We have a little ground to cover this morning. Please be seated."
    t "Muy bien, clase, guarden silencio. Tenemos material que cubrir hoy. Por favor, tomen asiento."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4927
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_bb4160af:

    # "The sound of our homeroom teacher's arrival forces me to stuff my phone back into my pants pocket."
    "El sonido de la llegada del maestro me obliga a meter mi teléfono en el bolsillo de mi pantalón."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4960
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_fb20c4e2:

    # "My phone is soon buzzing with Nozomi's reply, and it'll just have to wait. But it's going to be okay."
    "Mi celular pronto vibra con la respuesta de Nozomi, y tendrá que esperar. Pero todo estará bien."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4932
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_7f4bfab0:

    # "We're going to fix everything, Nozomi. You wait and see..."
    "Lo arreglaremos todo, Nozomi. Solo espera y verás..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4936
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_5dec2c09:

    # "When lunchtime rolls around, I get up from my desk to grab my food."
    "Cuando llega la hora del almuerzo, me levanto de mi escritorio para tomar mi comida."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4942
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_3a778d6e:

    # "... Only to immediately be stared down by those girls again." with dissolve
    "... Solo para inmediatamente ser confrontado por esas chicas otra vez." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4944
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f47cb4c9:

    # h "Guess rooftop club's cancelled today, huh."
    h "Supongo que el club de la azotea se cancela hoy, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4945
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_46929cf7:

    # ks frown "Oh for the love of... You girls know this is harassment, right?"
    ks frown "Oh, por el amor de... Saben que esto es acoso, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4947
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_2fbb4b47:

    # n irritated "And you wouldn't know anything about that, would you." with dissolve
    n irritated "No que tú sepas mucho de ese tema, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4949
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_d88c0353:

    # "I scoff at her. As if anything she has to say matters to me any more."
    "Le volteo los ojos. Como si lo que sea que tenga que decir me importara ahora."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4950
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_e237c932:

    # ks "I'm not going anywhere. But you're never going to keep us apart, no matter what you think."
    ks "No iré a ningún lado. Pero ustedes no van a mantenernos separados, sin importar lo que piensen."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4952
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_11cb7fe4:

    # ks "If... \"Akiko\" wants to see me, she will. It's her decision, not any of yours." with dissolve
    ks "Si... \"Akiko\" quiere verme, lo hará. Es su decisión, no de ustedes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4953
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_0bf14df3:

    # "Man, it took some effort to force that name out of my lips."
    "Caray, me tomó algo de esfuerzo sacar ese nombre de mis labios."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4954
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_184d57da:

    # "I don't want to think of her that way any more."
    "Ya no quiero pensar en ella de esa manera."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4955
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_584843f1:

    # s uniform_folded "After what we were witness to yesterday? It was plainly apparent you had some sort of hold over her." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "¿Después de lo que atestiguamos ayer? Quedó plenamente claro que tienes alguna clase de influencia sobre ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4956
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_07451c07:

    # "Folding my arms, I resolve myself to digging in and pleading ignorance."
    "Cruzándome de brazos, me decido a simplemente fingir ignorancia."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4957
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f521a47b:

    # ks "Yeah? What kind of \"hold\" am I supposed to have on her?"
    ks "¿Ah, sí? ¿Y qué clase de \"influencia\" se supone que tengo sobre ella?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4958
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_6e983024:

    # "It's not like any of them can prove anything, so I just have to endure this waste of my time."
    "No es como si ninguna de ellas pudiera probar nada. Solo tengo que aguantar esta pérdida de mi tiempo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4959
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_5a1a0b58:

    # ks "She's the student council president, and I'm just some nobody."
    ks "Es la presidenta del consejo estudiantil, y yo soy solo un don nadie."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4960
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_e417aa0c:

    # h uniform_headhold2 "H'yeah, you can say that again." with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 "Seh, di algo que no sepamos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4961
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b74ce7b3:

    # ks "We just talked a lot, and she had so much to say for herself."
    ks "Simplemente estuvimos hablando mucho, y ella tenía mucho que decir de sí misma."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4962
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_a33f764c:

    # ks "Like, did you know how insecure she's been this whole time? No, you didn't because you don't know her like I do."
    ks "Por ejemplo, ¿sabían lo insegura que se ha sentido todo este tiempo? No, claro que no sabían, porque no la conocen como yo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4964
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_6d4a330c:

    # s angry_right "If you actually knew her, you would understand she'd never so brazenly and recklessly endanger her standing with her peers!" with dissolve
    s angry_right "¡Si de verdad la conocieras, entenderías que ella nunca pondría en peligro su estatus con sus compañeros de forma tan descarada e insensata!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4965
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_be57aab7:

    # s frown_right "And let us not forget how the chosen object of her sudden obsession aligns so suspiciously with your own." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Y no hemos de olvidar cómo el objeto elegido de su súbita obsesión se alinea muy sospechosamente con el de la tuya." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4966
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_fa67e225:

    # s irritated "How you were able to convince such a strong-willed, confident woman to satiate your own selfish desires mystify me." with dissolve
    s irritated "El cómo fuiste capaz de convencer a una mujer tan llena de voluntad y confianza de saciar tus deseos egoístas me desconcierta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4967
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_aee56601:

    # ks "Yeah, well, stay mystified. Now can I get back to my lunch or do I have to listen to more of your crap?"
    ks "Sí, bueno, quédate desconcertada. Ahora, ¿me van a dejar almorzar o aún tengo más estupideces que escuchar?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4969
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_d6732e78:

    # n side frown "Okay, that's enough beating around the bush." with dissolve
    n side frown "Muy buen, ya basta de rodeos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4970
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_d70c3f78:

    # "Something about the way she's staring me down is making my spine stiffen."
    "Hay algo en la forma en la que me está mirando que hace que se me ponga tensa la espalda."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4971
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_eddf4d7f:

    # n irritated "Last week, you approached me with some kind of light. I think it would put all our minds at ease if you gave that light to us." with dissolve
    n irritated "La semana pasada, te acercaste a mí con una especie de linterna. Creo que todas estaríamos más tranquilas si nos la entregas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4972
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_9686f2c6:

    # ks confused "... What?!"
    ks confused "... ¡¿Qué?!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4973
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_5b1bb056:

    # "... I really should've seen this coming."
    "... De verdad debí ver esto venir."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4974
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_fc14fef3:

    # h angry "What's the matter, dipshit? That a problem?" with dissolve
    h angry "¿Qué sucede, pendejo? ¿Es eso un problema?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4975
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_eb9c16ca:

    # ks frown "I-it's just a light. What's it to you?"
    ks frown "E-es solo una linterna. ¿A ustedes qué les importa eso?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4976
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_d0ab57e9:

    # "She saw my light, and these girls are desperate to keep me and my Nozomi apart."
    "Ella vio mi linterna, y estas chicas están desesperadas por mantenernos a mí y a mi Nozomi separados."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4977
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_74716911:

    # n front2 determined "If it's just a light then what's *your* problem? Just hand it over." with dissolve
    n front2 determined "Si es solo una linterna, entonces ¿cuál es *tu* problema? Solo dánosla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4978
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_1acab14d:

    # "Of course they were going to bring this up."
    "Debí saber que iban a intentar esto."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4979
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_6b361757:

    # ks "I... don't have it."
    ks "No la... no la tengo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4981
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b9ad0dd1:

    # h uniform furious "LIAR!" with vpunch
    h uniform furious "¡MIENTES!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4983
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_7d500e17:

    # "Hiroko pounds her smallish fist on my desk and I reflexively bolt out of my chair."
    "Hiroko azota su pequeño puño contra mi escritorio y yo salto reflexivamente de mi silla."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4984
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f52e8243:

    # h angry_side "Man, I thought that shit about the light was weird an' all, but look at him pissing himself." with dissolve
    h angry_side "Caray, pensé que esa mierda de la luz sonaba rara, pero mírenlo cagado del pánico ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4985
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_52c3c60c:

    # "Are they really going to tackle me in the fucking classroom?"
    "¿De verdad van a atacarme en el puto salón de clases?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4987
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_e56a6b95:

    # ks angry "Get away from me! You've all gone nuts!" with dissolve
    ks angry "¡Aléjense de mí! ¡Se han vuelto locas todas!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4988
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_97ea02e0:

    # "And if they are, who's going to stop them? The teacher left us the moment the bell rang."
    "Y si lo hacen, ¿quién va a detenerlas? El profesor se fue tan pronto sonó la campana."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4989
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_46f058eb:

    # "As for the rest of my classmates looking down on us voyeuristically as they gossip amongst themselves..."
    "Y en cuanto al resto de mis compañeros que están de mirones e intercambiando susurros..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4990
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_2544c6d3:

    # s uniform "My, all this flailing over a pocket flashlight. Perhaps you were onto something after all, Nozomi." with dissolve
    s uniform "Vaya, ¿tanta agitación por una simple lámpara de bolsillo? Quizá tus especulaciones eran acertadas después de todo, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4991
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_c61facb2:

    # "I bet everyone's heard about the ruckus at the tennis court by now."
    "Apuesto a que todos ya escucharon del alboroto en la cancha de tenis."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4992
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_31978d09:

    # ks "I-I'm not gonna be bullied by the likes of you! Just lay off!"
    ks "¡N-no voy a dejar que me hostiguen así! ¡Déjenme en paz!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4993
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_82cf5667:

    # "Everyone's already picked a side, and it sure isn't mine."
    "Todos ya tomaron un bando, y estoy seguro de que no es el mío."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4994
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_fdce244f:

    # n angry "Hiroko, get his bag! It's time we ended this!" with dissolve
    n angry "¡Hiroko, trae su bolsa! ¡Es hora de terminar con esto!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:4997
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_d0d957c4:

    # "Acting on pure instinct, I snatch my bag from under the desk before that gremlin can lay her hands on it and push past my onlooking classmates as I escape." with dissolve
    "Actuando por puro instinto, saco mi bolsa de debajo del escritorio antes de que esa duendecilla pueda ponerle las manos encima y escapo, pasando entre mis compañeros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5001
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ccc46eed:

    # "And I keep running, all the way to the school entrance as my mind races." with dissolve
    "Y sigo corriendo hasta la entrada de la escuela con la mente acelerada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5002
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_d04df18c:

    # "Do I tell a teacher? What good will that do? They're probably as poisoned against me as everyone else in this goddamned school."
    "¿Le digo al profesor? ¿De qué servirá? Seguro también lo habrán puesto en mi contra como a todos en esta maldita escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5006
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f6751f82:

    # "So I keep running." with dissolve
    "Así que sigo corriendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5008
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_c0885c8b:

    # "And running... until my legs burn and my lungs can take no more." with shake
    "Y corriendo... hasta que las piernas me arden y mis pulmones ya no pueden más." with shake

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5010
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_d199aa02:

    # "They're not gonna follow me out here. Besides, they got what they wanted, didn't they?"
    "No me van a seguir hasta acá afuera. Además, ya tienen lo que querían, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5011
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_5328632c:

    # "I'm gonna have to answer for skipping school, and they got me away from Nozomi. I'm sure those assholes are happy about that."
    "Me meteré en problemas por saltarme la escuela, y consiguieron que me alejara de Nozomi. Estoy seguro de que esas cabronas estarán contentas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5013
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_02a85110:

    # "But as long as I still have my penlight safe in my pocket, nothing else matters."
    "Pero siempre y cuando aún tenga mi linterna a salvo en mi bolsillo, nada más importa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5016
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b30e6b71:

    # "They're not going to keep me away from Nozomi for long."
    "No me mantendrán alejado de Nozomi por mucho tiempo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5017
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_5a146306:

    # "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Sorry that won't work for me.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Lo siento no puedo.\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5018
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_310a0dac:

    # ks frown "Haaaah... w-what?"
    ks frown "Haaaah... ¿qu-qué?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5019
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ab483d01:

    # "I gaze at my phone screen with exasperation as I struggle for breath."
    "Miro la pantalla de mi teléfono con exasperación mientras trato de recobrar el aliento."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5020
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_7bc1e996:

    # "What does she mean she can't meet me at home? I'm so close to sealing the deal with her and now she's making things difficult for me!"
    "¿Cómo que no puede ir a verme a mi casa? ¡Estoy así de cerca de solucionarlo todo y ahora me pone las cosas difíciles!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5021
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_7ba547dc:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"We need to meet up for a talk TODAY. This is urgent.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Tenemos que vernos y hablar HOY. Esto es urgente.\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5022
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_19a9c9d7:

    # "She CAN'T turn me down! She... she WANTS to speak to me, she HAS to!"
    "¡No puede rechazarme! ¡Ella... ella QUIERE hablar conmigo, TIENE que quererlo!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5024
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_2fcb244c:

    # "I can't bring my penlight back to school again after today. Not unless I want to risk those bitches stealing it from me."
    "No puedo llevar mi linterna a la escuela otra vez después de hoy. No a menos que quiera arriesgarme a que esas perras me la roben."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5026
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ddec52fa:

    # "... You better come through for me, Nozomi. Goddammit."
    "... Más te vale decirme que sí, Nozomi. Maldita sea."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5029
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_4aa77e87:

    # "{color=#5F5C5C}\"You're right we do need to talk. I'll be really busy with SC but i can get us that science classroom again, you remember which one? We can talk there when Im free\"{/color}"
    "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Tienes razón tenemos que hablar. Estare muy ocupada con el CE pero puedo conseguirnos el salón de ciencias, recuerdas cual? Podemos hablar ahí cuando tenga tiempo\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5031
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_eef85a6b:

    # "That's... right. It's not that she won't see me. She just had a good reason for turning me down."
    "Es... cierto. No es que no quiera verme. Simplemente tenía una buena razón por la que no podría a cualquier hora."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5032
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_21113e00:

    # "I guess she can't get away from her student council duties, can't stay out too late..."
    "Supongo que no puede escapar de sus deberes con el consejo estudiantil y no puede ausentarse hasta tarde..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5033
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_785182e2:

    # "This is going to make things more difficult. But I can work with this."
    "Así las cosas van a complicarse. Pero puedo trabajar con esto."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5034
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_d0fada14:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"Ok I'll be there. Let me know when you're free.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Muy bien, ahí estaré. Avísame cuando estés libre.\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5036
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_e8e5ab77:

    # "I can wait out the rest of the day, and I thank my lucky stars my dad won't be around to lecture me about truancy until he's back from work."
    "Puedo esperar el resto del día, y gracias al cielo tengo la suerte de que mi papá no estará para regañarme por salirme de la escuela hasta que regrese del trabajo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5038
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_8b234373:

    # "All I have to do is sneak back into school, meet Nozomi again and hypnotize her. Take away that silly compulsion to worship the ground her doppelganger walks on."
    "Solo debo escabullirme de vuelta a la escuela, encontrarme con Nozomi e hipnotizarla. Quitarle ese absurdo impulso de venerar el suelo sobre el que su doble camina."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5039
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b67697de:

    # "She has nothing more to learn from her. My Nozomi's perfect just the way she is now."
    "No tiene nada más que aprender de ella. Mi Nozomi es perfecta tal como es."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5043
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_c0c0751b:

    # "{color=#5F5C5C}\"I'll be out in 5 mins. Can't wait to see you again\"{/color}"
    "{color=#5F5C5C}\"Estaré libre en 5 mins. No puedo esperar a volver a verte\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5045
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_c70874a9:

    # "I'll make her see that. I'll be the only one she loves around here."
    "La haré ver eso. Seré el único a quien ame por aquí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5048
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_029d11a2:

    # "As soon as Nozomi sent me that text, I was ready to head out and dash back to school."
    "Cuando Nozomi me mandó ese mensaje, ya estaba listo para salir directo a la escuela."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5049
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_11901869:

    # "I come to a stop by the gates, and... coast is clear."
    "Me detengo en las puertas, y... no hay moros en la costa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5050
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_cb652172:

    # "It's pretty late now so most of the after school clubs have cleared out, which should include those other girls."
    "Ya es bastante tarde, por lo que casi todos ya se fueron de sus clubes, lo cual debería incluir a esas chicas."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5051
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_8bb285fb:

    # "And I don't think anyone else is going to recognise me around here."
    "No creo que nadie más vaya a reconocerme por aquí."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5053
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_e19892f1:

    # "So I slip back inside and walk the corridors until I reach the science classroom."
    "Así que me escabullo y camino por los pasillos hasta llegar al salón de ciencias."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5055
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b9d9ff45:

    # "With one hand in my pocket, my breath catches as I tap my knuckles against the door in anticipation..."
    "Con una mano en el bolsillo, aguanto el aliento con anticipación al golpear la puerta con mis nudillos..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5056
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_1c4e38ac:

    # ks confused "N-Nozomi? Are you in there?"
    ks confused "¿N-Nozomi? ¿Estás ahí?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5057
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_cc2132cb:

    # a "{size=16}... I'm here.{/size}"
    a "{size=16}... Aquí estoy.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5058
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_7def7d86:

    # "It feels oddly nostalgic to be back here, where Nozomi's journey towards perfection began just a short week ago."
    "Se siente extrañamente nostálgico regresar aquí, donde el viaje de Nozomi hacia la perfección comenzó hace solo una semana."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5059
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_22dd6143:

    # "I suppose it's fitting that this is where she completes it. Where she becomes the best that she can be."
    "Supongo que es adecuando que aquí sea donde lo complete. Donde se convirtió en la mejor que puede ser."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5062
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_793fbe21:

    # "With me..."
    "Conmigo..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5064
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f95310b9:

    # ks confused "... Nozomi?"
    ks confused "... ¿Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5067
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_74d36c5d:

    # ks "What's going on? Aren't you going to face me?"
    ks "¿Qué pasa? ¿No vas a voltear a verme?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5068
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_bd144539:

    # "That's her alright, but for some reason her back is turned and her head is lowered towards the floor like she's... dejected?"
    "Definitivamente es ella, pero por alguna razón está de espaldas y con la cabeza agachada, como si estuviera... ¿abatida?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5069
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_fe21cd3c:

    # "Isn't she happy to see me?"
    "¿Acaso no está feliz de verme?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5070
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_47e81af5:

    # a "... They're kicking me out of the student council."
    a "... Van a sacarme del consejo estudiantil."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5071
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_47a02313:

    # ks "I... oh..."
    ks "Te... oh..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5072
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_3d4c72b0:

    # a "{size=16}Yeah.{/size}"
    a "{size=16}Sí.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5073
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_9d8ffcb9:

    # "Guess that explains the vibe in here, but... no, I can't allow myself to get distracted."
    "Supongo que eso explica la vibra que hay aquí, pero... no, no puedo distraerme ahora."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5074
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_b48171ee:

    # a "Right now they're all in the other room debating my position as president, so I had to excuse myself."
    a "Ahora mismo están en el otro salón debatiendo mi posición como presidenta, así que tuve que salir del aula."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5075
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_0c62eda6:

    # "We knew this going to happen."
    "Sabíamos que esto iba a pasar."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5076
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ccf681d7:

    # a "It's so humiliating. I don't know why they're bothering to drag it out."
    a "Es tan humillante. No sé por qué se molestan en alargarlo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5077
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_631809cb:

    # "None of these assholes were going to accept what she's become. We knew that."
    "Ninguno de estos hijos de puta iba a aceptar en lo que se ha convertido. Eso lo sabíamos."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5078
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_c475a201:

    # ks neutral "You don't need it, Nozomi. You don't need them; you don't have to be accountable to anyone anymore."
    ks neutral "No lo necesitas, Nozomi. Y no los necesitas a ellos; ya no tienes que ajustarte a lo que otros quieren."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5079
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ee6e4e27:

    # ks "You just have to be Nozomi. Be the best you can be."
    ks "Solo tienes que ser Nozomi. Ser la mejor tú que puedas ser."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5080
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ebe26fda:

    # a "Yup... I'll be the best version of me..."
    a "Sipi... Seré la mejor versión de mí..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5081
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_fd2787b4:

    # "I pull the penlight out of my pocket and click it on, as I smile encouragingly at the back of her pretty head."
    "Saco la linterna de mi bolsillo y la enciendo, poniendo una alentadora sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5082
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_6ccb6820:

    # ks smile "And I'll be right here with you, every step of the way."
    ks smile "Y yo estaré aquí contigo a cada paso que des."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5083
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_c021fa73:

    # ks "Now come on, turn around. I want to see your face again. I want to hypnotize you."
    ks "Ahora date la vuelta, ¿sí? Quiero ver tu bello rostro otra vez. Quiero hipnotizarte."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5084
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_cff1faa9:

    # ks "That'll cheer you up, right? You always enjoy hypnosis."
    ks "Eso te animará, ¿verdad? Sé cuánto disfrutas la hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5085
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_9d4a9bc1:

    # a "Eheh..."
    a "Ejeje..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5086
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_a3a74fea:

    # a "... Do I?"
    a "... ¿Te parece?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5087
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ac6adbc1:

    # ks neutral "Hm?"
    ks neutral "¿Mm?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5088
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_3eade238:

    # a "I guess Nozomi enjoys it..."
    a "Supongo que Nozomi la disfruta..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5090
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_38ef9395:

    # a uniform3 frown "... But I'm not Nozomi. Am I." with dissolve
    a uniform3 frown "... Pero yo no soy Nozomi. ¿Verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5091
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_3abe129b:

    # ks confused "... What?"
    ks confused "... ¿Qué?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5092
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_5c366bb2:

    # "For a moment I stand frozen in time as she turns to me and delivers those words that cut straight to my heart."
    "Por un momento me quedo congelado al verla darse la vuelta y decir esas palabras que se encajan directo en mi corazón."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5093
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_e062f9ea:

    # ks "Don't... say that. Nozomi, don't listen to what people tell you!"
    ks "No... digas eso. ¡Nozomi, no escuches lo que la gente te dice!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5095
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_a899a4bd:

    # a frown_side "People tell me I'm annoying. That I'm too pushy, too weird..." with dissolve
    a frown_side "La gente me dice que soy molesta. Que soy demasiado entrometida, demasiado rara..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5096
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_91034249:

    # a frown "Too trusting..." with dissolve
    a frown "Demasiado confiada..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5097
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_031b5d10:

    # "She has a glare in her eyes as she speaks. A look toward me that I haven't seen since..."
    "Habla con una intensa mirada. Una mirada que no la había visto darme desde..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5098
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_c10255cd:

    # a sleep "People are jerks, aren't they. We're always finding ways to tear each other down to the ground." with dissolve
    a sleep "La gente es cruel, ¿verdad? Siempre encontramos formas de tirarnos al suelo unos a otros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5099
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f13a5e92:

    # "Wait, what is happening? Why is she talking like she's... not Nozomi?"
    "Espera, ¿qué está pasando? ¿Por qué está hablando como si... no fuera Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5100
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_84cabcfd:

    # a uniform_down3 armband_down sad_closed2 "And it's so... so tempting to stay down there. Think it's where you belong, that you can be no better." with dissolve
    a uniform_down3 armband_down sad_closed2 "Y es muy... muy tentador quedarse ahí tirado. Pensar que allí es donde perteneces, que no puedes ser mejor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5101
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_0fe6dc82:

    # "She couldn't... there's no way she can reject everything I told her. Not after everything I've proved, not after everything we've been through together."
    "No puede haber... es imposible que rechazara todo lo que le dije. No después de todo lo que he comprobado, no después de todo por lo que hemos pasado."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5102
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_4cdb69d9:

    # a neutral "In a way, Koyama, I can almost understand you." with dissolve
    a neutral "De cierta forma, Koyama, casi puedo comprenderte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5103
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_ba4d2b32:

    # "It's not... it's not POSSIBLE!"
    "No es... ¡no es POSIBLE!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5104
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_5eeb6dec:

    # ks surprised "{cps=15}N-now, Nozomi, just listen to me-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks surprised "{cps=15}A-a ver, Nozomi, solo escúchame-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5108
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_558492b5:

    # "But she's not listening to me! As I go to raise my lit penlight aloft, she crouches down to the floor and bows her head..."
    "¡Pero no me está escuchando! Y cuando alzo mi linterna encendida, ella se agacha al suelo y hace una reverencia..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5109
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_70fea418:

    # a "But I'll never be like you. I don't pity myself every time I get knocked down."
    a "Pero yo nunca seré como tú. Yo no me autocompadezco cada vez que caigo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5110
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_8814ba84:

    # "And as she does so, her hand closes around something I only just now notice is lying in wait by her feet..."
    "Y tras hacer eso, su mano envuelve algo que apenas ahora noto que se encontraba yaciendo junto a sus pies..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5111
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_f4f467b1:

    # a "I'd never try to bring others down with me. Exploit them, gaslight them... until they're every bit as dirty as me."
    a "Nunca intentaría arrastrar a otros al suelo conmigo. Explotarlos, manipularlos... hasta que estén tan sucios y llenos de polvo como yo."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5112
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_12c1a809:

    # "It's a..."
    "Es una..."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5113
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_eaf01dd8:

    # a "I'll never wallow around in the dirt."
    a "Nunca me revolcaré en la tierra."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5116
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_8a3ab108:

    # a uniform3 frown armband "Because I always get back up!" with vpunch
    a uniform3 frown armband "¡Porque yo siempre me levanto!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5121
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_264fde10:

    # "She rises, and I'm forced to step back as I suddenly find myself staring down at the point of a weighty-looking bamboo sword."
    "Ella se alza, y me veo obligado a dar un paso atrás, viendo de repente frente a mí la punta de una visiblemente robusta espada de bambú."

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5122
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_7af1f804:

    # ks angry "W-what are you doing?! Nozomi!"
    ks angry "¡¿Qu-qué estás haciendo?! ¡Nozomi!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5123
translate spanish Day8_Villain2_Kyou_5f6a1e22:

    # "This is crazy! She really brought that fucking thing to school?! I have to..."
    "¡Esto es una locura! ¡¿De verdad trajo esa puta cosa a la escuela?!"

# game/Kyou 8.rpy:5125
